%20cruise%20lines%2C%20or%20cruise%20ships%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20cater%20to%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20clientele.%20Some%20brands%20are%20popular%20among%20young%20party-goers%2C%20while%20others%20may%20attract%20a%20more%20mature%20crowd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20get%20paired%20up%20and%20matched%20with%20the%20right%20cruise%20line.%20It%20can%20make%20a%20tremendous%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Chiron%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20book%20something%20that%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20your%20likes%20and%20desires.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Don't%20get%20distracted%20by%20flashy%20sales%20and%20packages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20cruises%20offer%20shipboard%20credit%20or%20package%20deals%20for%20food%2C%20drinks%2C%20or%20other%20items%20and%20services.%20Princess%20cruises%2C%20for%20example%2C%20charges%20%2476.70%20daily%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db2a41f81d34bdb9519318bb11826eb679eadd711f38e2626d53e635474030b35%26postID%3D64ac29c340c6c45887031ae5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.princess.com%252Fships-and-experience%252Ffood-and-dining%252Fbeverages%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrink%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20provides%20up%20to%2015%20alcoholic%20beverages%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20get%20caught%20up%20with%20some%20of%20these%20sales.%20It's%20the%20same%20offers%20and%20they're%20just%20getting%20regurgitated%20and%20re-titled%2C%26quot%3B%20Chiron%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they're%20creating%20distractions%20and%20sometimes%20they're%20covering%20for%20higher%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20with%20the%20drink%20package%2C%20when%20you%20calculate%20how%20much%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20drink%20in%20order%20to%20break%20even%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20If%20you're%20traveling%20with%20children%2C%20look%20for%20family-friendly%20cruises%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20ships%20that%20are%20just%20really%20incredible%20for%20kids%20and%20there%20are%20ships%20that%20aren't%2C%26quot%3B%20Chiron%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20ships%20have%20amenities%20tailored%20for%20kids%20like%20water%20parks%2C%20teen%20clubs%2C%20kids%20menus%2C%20and%20day%20care%20options%2C%20while%20other%20ships%20are%20far%20less%20accommodating%20toward%20young%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20First-timers%20should%20consider%20booking%20through%20a%20travel%20agent%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20advice%20Chiron%20said%20he%20gives%20first-time%20cruise-goers%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bresearch%20online%2C%20but%20don't%20book%20online.%26quot%3B%20Unlike%20airfare%2C%20booking%20a%20cruise%20can%20be%20an%20overwhelming%20and%20manual%20process%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20travel%20agents%20who%20have%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20cruise%20lines%20have%20access%20to%20special%20rates%20and%20can%20advocate%20on%20your%20behalf%20if%20something%20goes%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20not%20wind%20up%20in%20the%20type%20of%20cabin%20you%20want%2C%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20the%20reservation%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20could%20go%20wrong%20or%20things%20that%20%5Ba%20travel%20agent%5D%20can%20help%20improve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Buy%20travel%20insurance%20if%20you're%20going%20on%20an%20international%20cruise%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EChiron%20said%20he%20never%20travels%20internationally%20without%20purchasing%20trip%20insurance.%20But%20what's%20even%20more%20important%20than%20buying%20insurance%20is%20understanding%20exactly%20what%20it%20covers%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20trip%20interruption%20and%20cancellation%20insurance%20to%20evacuation%20and%20property%20coverage%2C%20not%20all%20insurance%20policies%20are%20made%20equal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20medical%20insurance%20that%20does%20not%20cover%20international%20travel%20which%20is%20very%20important%20for%20people%20to%20find%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20passengers%20who%20see%20a%20doctor%20abroad%20for%20something%20simple%C2%A0could%20end%20up%20footing%20a%20%24500%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Weigh%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20booking%20airfare%20through%20the%20cruise%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cruise%20lines%20have%20access%20to%20discounted%20flights%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20bundle%20your%20airfare%20with%20your%20cruise.%20But%20like%20all%20third-party%20booking%20platforms%2C%20the%20programs%20have%20their%20benefits%20and%20downsides.%20Chiron%C2%A0recommends%20comparing%20the%20flight%20prices%20and%20availability%20of%20booking%20directly%20with%20the%20airline%20to%20whatever%20the%20cruise%20line%20is%20offering%20before%20making%20a%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Arrive%20at%20the%20port%20at%20least%20a%20day%20before%20the%20cruise%20departs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20a%20good%20rule%20of%20thumb%20to%20arrive%20at%20least%20one%20day%20before%20your%20cruise%20departs%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20flying%20to%20the%20port.%20That%20way%2C%20you%20have%20more%20flexibility%20if%20your%20flight%20gets%20delayed%20or%20canceled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20domestic%20ports%20like%20Miami%2C%20Seattle%2C%20or%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20it's%20fine%20to%20arrive%20a%20day%20before%20your%20cruise%20departs%2C%20Chiron%20said.%20But%20for%20cruises%20departing%20from%20international%20ports%2C%20you%20should%20consider%20arriving%20multiple%20days%20in%20advance%2C%20he%20said.%20That%20way%2C%20you%20can%20explore%20the%20area%20and%20adjust%20to%20the%20time%20difference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20depends%20where%20I'm%20going.%20I%20enjoy%20Rome%2C%20so%20sometimes%20I'll%20go%20in%20two%20or%20three%20days%20before%20the%20cruise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20going%20to%20the%20Mediterranean%2C%20why%20wouldn't%20you%20want%20to%20spend%20some%20extra%20time%20in%20whatever%20port%20you're%20departing%20out%20of%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E8.%20P%3Cstrong%3Elan%20strategically%20to%20avoid%20long%20lines%20and%20crowded%20ports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20are%20cruise%20ships%20booked%20to%20capacity%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cities%20that%20they're%20visiting%20are%20overflowing%20with%20tourists%20too.%20This%20congestion%20at%20cruise%20ports%20can%20cause%20some%20challenges%20as%20cruisers%20disembark%2C%20Chiron%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Santorini%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20said%20cruise%20passengers%20are%20required%20to%20take%20a%20smaller%20tender%20boat%20to%20shore%2C%20and%20then%20hop%20on%20a%20tram%20in%20order%20to%20get%20to%20town.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20got%20off%20the%20tender%20I%20saw%20thousands%20of%20people%20waiting%20in%20line%20to%20take%20a%20tram%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20actually%20got%20back%20on%20the%20tender%2C%20went%20back%20to%20the%20ship%2C%20had%20lunch%2C%20waited%20a%20couple%20hours%20and%20then%20came%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20advice%3A%C2%A0%26quot%3BTake%20some%20time%20to%20do%20research%20on%20how%20some%20of%20these%20ports%20are%20handling%20cruise%20passengers%20and%20tourist%20traffic%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20plan%20strategically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Don't%20feel%20pressure%20to%20disembark%20at%20every%20port%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20potentially%20controversial%20travel%20hack%20of%20Chiron's%20is%20to%20skip%20disembarkment%20at%20the%20ports%20he's%20already%20been%20to%20in%20order%20to%20enjoy%20the%20amenit