a%20Party%20for%20having%20lost%20the%20Karnataka%20election%20miserably.%C2%A0%20Another%20reason%20why%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20unwilling%20to%20sell%20rice%20to%20states%20is%20because%20approximately%2086%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20fuel%20needs%20are%20said%20to%20be%20met%20by%20imports.%20Hence%20to%20reduce%20this%20dependence%20on%20imports%2C%20the%20government%20is%20pushing%20for%20ethanol%20production%20from%20rice%20for%20blending%20it%20with%20petrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20not%20a%20gross%20irony%20that%20for%20ethanol%20production%2C%20the%20government%20has%20fixed%20the%20price%20of%20rice%20at%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20quintal%2C%20whereas%20it%20is%20sold%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%203%2C400%20per%20quintal%20to%20state%20governments%20to%20meet%20the%20food%20security%20of%20their%20citizens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20amount%20of%20rice%20sold%20for%20ethanol%20production%20is%20reportedly%20six%20times%20higher%20than%20that%20sold%20to%20all%20the%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20the%20needs%20of%20cars%20for%20fuel%20to%20be%20prioritised%20over%20food%20for%20the%20hungry%20and%20malnourished%20millions%20of%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20refusal%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20made%20many%20in%20Karnataka%20question%20whether%20buying%20more%20rice%20produced%20by%20distant%20states%20should%20be%20the%20way%20forward.%20Instead%2C%20say%20agriculture%20experts%20such%20as%20Prakash%20Kammardi%2C%20former%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Agriculture%20Prices%20Commission%20(KAPC)%2C%20the%20state%20government%20should%20explore%20procurement%20of%20Ragi%20and%20Jowar%C2%A0locally%20by%20paying%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20to%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20instead%20of%20importing%20rice%20from%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1-300x161.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-646849%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22551%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20man%20holding%20PDS%20rice.%20Photo%3A%20Adithyan%20P.C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20put%20the%20Rs.%2010%2C000%20crore%20estimated%20for%20importing%20rice%20from%20outside%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20instead.%20The%20recent%20statement%20by%20CM%20Siddaramaiah%20himself%20that%20only%2025%25%20of%20the%20rural%20population%20of%20Karnataka%20eats%20rice%20and%20that%2075%25%20of%20them%20eat%20Ragi%C2%A0and%C2%A0Jowar%20and%20that%20this%2075%25%20eats%20rice%20only%20on%20festival%20days%2C%20has%20fuelled%20efforts%20to%20rethink%20the%20whole%20strategy.%20Further%2C%20growing%20millets%20consumes%20very%20little%20water%20and%20is%20hence%20an%20environment%20friendly%20measure%20to%20adopt%20in%20view%20of%20the%20current%20water%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20announcements%20that%20incentives%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20increase%20production%20of%20Ragi%20and%20Jowar%20by%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20to%20give%20these%20grains%20through%20the%20PDS%20have%20been%20made%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20without%20concrete%20action%20being%20taken%20about%20it.%20The%20government%20and%20Kammardi%20have%20both%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20government%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20procure%202.28%20lakh%20tonnes%20a%20month%20of%20Ragi%20and%20Jowar%20immediately%20as%20their%20current%20supply%20is%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fafter-cancelling-karnataka-rice-order-fci-sees-few-auction-takers%5C%22%3EWeeks%20After%20It%20Denied%20Rice%20to%20Karnataka%2C%20FCI%20Faces%20Low%20Turnout%20in%20Auction%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShockingly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fstate%2Ftop-karnataka-stories%2Fdespite-demand-area-under-millets-shrinks-in-karnataka-1234654.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20on%20July%207%20that%20the%20area%20under%20millets%20in%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20actually%20been%20going%20down%20over%20the%20years.%20Data%20from%20the%20agriculture%20department%20shows%20that%20the%20area%20under%20millets%20has%20declined%20from%2021%20lakh%20hectares%20(ha)%20in%202017-18%20to%2016%20lakh%20ha%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20production%20has%20come%20down%20from%2032%20lakh%20tonnes%20to%2021%20lakh%20tonnes.%C2%A0%20This%2C%20when%20the%20world%20is%20celebrating%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reasons%20cited%20for%20the%20reduced%20production%20of%20millets%20are%20inadequate%20procurement%20and%20distribution%20of%20the%20crop%20by%20the%20government%2C%20lack%20of%20processing%20and%20marketing%20facilities%2C%20and%20unstable%20prices.%20Though%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA)%20to%20bring%20millets%20under%20the%20PDS%2C%20this%20provision%20has%20hardly%20been%20made%20use%20of.%20So%2C%20there%20is%20great%20potential%20to%20increase%20the%20area%20under%20millets%20in%20Karnataka.%20If%20only%20the%20government%20makes%20known%20its%20desire%20to%20procure%20millets%20at%20the%20MSP%2C%20farmers%20will%20increase%20their%20production.%20And%20the%20government%20may%20be%20able%20to%20procure%20the%20full%20required%20amount%20by%20the%20end%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20have%20to%20give%20the%20farmers%20Rs%2050%20per%20kilo%20for%20Ragi%20and%20Rs.%2043%20per%20kilo%20for%20Jowar%20(the%20MSP%20as%20per%20the%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20Committee%20formula%20of%20cost%20of%20inputs%20plus%2050%25)%2C%20as%20per%20a%20detailed%20study%20by%20the%20KAPC%20in%202014%2C%20according%20to%20Kammardi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20price%20would%20not%20be%20very%20much%20more%20than%20what%20the%20government%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20rice%20procured%20from%20the%20Union%2C%20as%20the%20real%20economic%20cost%20of%20this%20rice%20would%20be%20Rs%2043%20per%20kilo%2C%20plus%20the%20cost%20of%20transportation%2C%20according%20to%20Kammardi.%20Also%2C%20if%2010%20kilo%20of%20rice%20is%20given%20to%20each%20individual%20who%20does%20not%20really%20eat%20it%2C%20this%20would%20only%20aggravate%20the%20issue%20of%20PDS%20rice%20being%20sold%20in%20the%20black%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20similar%20incentive%20is%20provided%20to%20north%20Karnataka%20farmers%20with%20the%20assurance%20that%20MSP%20will%20be%20paid%20for%20toor%C2%A0and%20other%20dals%20and%20oilseeds%20to%20be%20distributed%20through%20the%20PDS%20along%20with%20the%C2%A0Ragi%C2%A0and%C2%A0Jowar%2C%20these%20measures%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20total%20development%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20farmers%2C%20who%20are%20in%20distress%20currently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F22195751%2F2020_5img19_May_2020_PTI19-05-2020_000090B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F22195751%2F2020_5img19_May_2020_PTI19-05-2020_000090B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F22195751%2F2020_5img19_May_2020_PTI19-05-2020_000090B-300x215.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F22195751%2F2020_5img19_May_2020_PTI19-05-2020_000090B-1024x732.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-456086%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20farmer%20throws%20away%20tomatoes%20he%20grew%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Karad%2C%20after%20prices%20crashed%20because%20of%20rumours%20around%20the%20spread%20of%20coronavirus.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20frequent%20upheavals%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20agriculture%20products%20are%20a%20great%20source%20of%20distress%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20farmers%20were%20throwing%20the%20tomatoes%20they%20had%20grown%20on%20the%20road%20as%20they%20failed%20to%20get%20remunerative%20prices%20for%20them.%C2%A0%20But%20now%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20sudden%20surge%20in%20the%20prices%20of%20tomatoes%2C%20which%20has%20reached%20prices%20of%20Rs.%20130%20per%20kilo%20in%20many%20places.%C2%A0%20The%20same%20situation%20prevails%20in%20the%20price%20of%20toor%20dal%2C%20the%20mainstay%20source%20of%20protein%20for%20most%20families%2C%20which%20has%20reportedly%20increased%20by%207.8%25%20to%20Rs.%20130.75%20per%20kilo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20putting%20stock%20limits%20on%20urad%C2%A0and%C2%A0toor%20dal%20to%20prevent%20hoarding%20seems%20to%20have%20had%20hardly%20any%20effect%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20price%20rise%20of%20dals.%20But%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20rise%20in%20market%20prices%20of%20these%20food%20items%20hardly%20benefits%20farmers%2C%20most%20of%20it%20going%20to%20the%20pockets%20of%20middlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-accidental-pioneer-cash-transfers-for-food%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20Becomes%20an%20Accidental%20Pioneer%20of%20Cash%20Transfers%20for%20Food%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudy%20recommends%20storage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20detailed%20study%20conducted%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Plantation%20Management%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20KAPC%20in%20September%202019%2C%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%98Group%20Approach%20on%20Marketing%20of%20Farm%20Commodities%3A%20A%20Roadmap%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%2C%20says%20that%20an%20effective%20way%20of%20stabilising%20prices%20of%20food%20products%2C%20especially%20of%20perishables%20such%20as%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20is%20to%20increase%20the%20storage%20facilities%20for%20them%20so%20that%20farmers%20are%20able%20to%20store%20them%20safely%20until%20markets%20become%20more%20benign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20recommends%20collectivisation%20of%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20through%20Farmer-Producer%20Companies%20(FPCs)%20or%20Farmer-Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%20which%20will%20enable%20them%20to%20invest%20jointly%20in%20machinery%2C%20common%20collection%20centres%2C%20storage%20godowns%2C%20transportation%2C%20marketing%2C%20value%20addition%20through%20food%20processing%2C%20etc.%2C%20to%20achieve%20greater%20bargaining%20power%2C%20economies%20of%20scale%2C%20and%20avoid%20steep%20fall%20in%20prices.%20While%20some%20incentives%20are%20proposed%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20budget%20towards%20this%2C%20much%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FBudget_carousel-copy.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farmers%20were%20unable%20to%20sell%20there%20produce%20for%20a%20good%20price%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20cash%20after%20demonetisation.%20Representative%20image%20credit%3A%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222036%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-104254%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22666%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EProcuring%20millets%2C%20dals%2C%20milk%2C%20eggs%2C%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20locally%20from%20farmers%E2%80%99%20cooperatives%20and%20distributing%20these%20items%20through%20the%20PDS%20and%20to%20Anganwadis%20and%20schools%20will%20reduce%20the%20malnutrition%20levels.%20Representative%20image%20credit%3A%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProcuring%20millets%2C%20dals%2C%20milk%2C%20eggs%2C%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20locally%20from%20farmers%E2%80%99%20cooperatives%20and%20distributing%20these%20items%20through%20the%20PDS%20and%20to%20Anganwadis%20and%20schools%20will%20reduce%20the%20malnutrition%20levels%20across%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20languishing%20behind%20other%20southern%20states%20in%20nutrition%20levels.%20The%20Hyderabad-based%20National%20Nutrition%20Monitoring%20Bureau%20has%20recommended%20that%20a%20healthy%20person%20requires%2010%20kilo%20of%20food%20grains%20a%20month.%C2%A0%20This%20has%20been%20the%20ask%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Food%20Campaign%20as%20well%2C%20which%20has%20demanded%20that%20in%20addition%20to%2010%20kilo%20food%20grains%2C%201.5%20kilo%20of%20dal%20and%20800%20gram%20of%20oil%20per%20person%20per%20month%20should%20be%20provided%20through%20the%20PDS.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20Rough%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20farmers%20will%20get%2045%25%20more%20for%20their%20toor%20dal%C2%A0and%20oil%20seeds%C2%A0if%20government%20procures%20it%20at%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0survey%20in%20March%202023%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20most%20impoverished%20district%2C%20Yadgir%2C%C2%A0by%20the%20Auro%20Society%20for%20Public%20Nutrition%2C%20Public%20Health%20and%20Public%20Policy%2C%C2%A0revealed%20that%C2%A064%25%20of%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%20three%20were%20either%20stunted%2C%20wasted%20or%20underweight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Karnataka%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20well-developed%20state%2C%20poverty%20and%20malnutrition%20are%20a%20major%20challenge%20in%20at%20least%2010%20districts%2C%20says%20the%20survey%20result.%20The%20survey%20report%20has%20suggested%20that%20the%20government%20should%20focus%20on%20agricultural%20interventions%20to%20increase%20farm%20productivity%20and%20thereby%20lift%20at%20least%2020%25%20of%20the%20population%20above%20poverty%20level%20in%20Yadgir%2C%20Raichur%20and%20Kalaburagi.%20The%20findings%20of%20the%20report%20only%20confirm%20that%20investing%20in%20the%20farmers%20of%20North%20Karnataka%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20for%20removing%20their%20poverty%20and%20reversing%20the%20neglect%20of%20the%20North%20Karnataka%20region%20by%20successive%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20itself%20will%20prosper%20as%20the%20additional%20money%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20its%20farmers%20will%20boost%20local%20economies%20instead%20of%20going%20to%20the%20farmers%20of%20other%20states.%20Is%20this%20not%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20for%20the%20new%20Congress%20government%20to%20show%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20Karnataka%20will%20increase%20the%20income%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20substantially%20before%20its%20five-year%20term%20ends%3F%20This%20is%20the%20best%20%E2%80%98guarantee%E2%80%99%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20can%20assure%20to%20Kannadigas.%20This%20would%20be%20a%20sure-fire%20strategy%20for%20the%20Congress%20government%20to%20win%20the%20election%20again%20in%202028%2C%20since%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20failed%20miserably%20in%20fulfilling%20the%20promise%20to%20double%20farmers%E2%80%99%20incomes%20that%20it%20made%20in%202014%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKathyayini%20Chamaraj%20is%20the%20Executive%20Trustee%20of%20CIVIC-Bangalore%20and%20an%20associate%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Food%20Campaign.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a