20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20now%20called%20an%20emergency%20meeting.%20He%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20Delhi%20government%20is%20prepared%20to%20tackle%20every%20situation%20caused%20by%20the%20monsoon%20fury.%C2%A0Delhi%20Police%20has%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20public%20gathering%20in%20the%20flood-prone%C2%A0areas%C2%A0as%20a%20precautionary%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2011%20am%2C%20the%20river%20was%20flowing%20at%20207.38%20at%20Old%20Railway%20Bridge.%20This%20was%20higher%20than%20the%202013%20water%20level%20of%20207.32%2C%20when%20the%20national%20capital%20saw%20flooding.%20In%201978%2C%20the%20Yamuna%20had%20flowed%20at%20207.49%20metres%2C%20a%20record%20that%20was%20broken%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20from%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20have%20predicted%20that%20the%20water%20level%20may%20rise%20further%2C%20reaching%20207.57%20metres%20later%20in%20the%20day.%20The%20consistent%20rise%20will%20prompt%20an%20extreme%20flood%20alert%20in%20Old%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20has%20recorded%20a%20rapid%20rise%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20level%20over%20the%20past%20three%20days.%20The%20administration%20has%20relocated%20people%20living%20in%20the%20flood-prone%20areas%20and%20shut%20the%20Old%20Railway%20Bridge%20for%20traffic%20and%20train%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20PTI%20report%2C%20an%20official%20has%20said%20the%20sharp%20rise%20in%20water%20level%20was%20due%20to%20continuous%20rainfall%20in%20upper%20catchment%20areas%20and%20saturated%20soil%20from%20heavy%20precipitation%20in%20Delhi%20and%20nearby%20regions.%20Water%20released%20from%20overflowing%20dams%20in%20Haryana%20have%20led%20to%20the%20surge%20in%20Yamuna%20levels.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoats%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20spread%20awareness%20along%20river%20banks%20and%20for%20rescue%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20homes%20near%20the%20bank%20have%20been%20flooded.%20NDTV%20spoke%20to%20shopowners%20in%20