20to%20sell%2086.4%25%20of%20their%20Mach-E%20inventory%20within%2030%20days%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202022%2C%20but%20that%20figure%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20a%20turn%20rate%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20dropped%20to%2027.7%25%20in%20the%20same%20period%20of%202023%20even%20as%20the%20automaker%20had%20over%20twice%20as%20much%20inventory%20on%20the%20market%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-inventory-most-least-dealerships-availability-hyundai-kia-2023-6%23ford-mustang-mach-e-4%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20analytics%20firm%20Cloud%20Theory%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.ford.com%2Fcontent%2Ffordmedia%2Ffna%2Fus%2Fen%2Fnews%2F2023%2F07%2F06%2Fford-continues-its-sales-momentum-as-americas-no--1-brand--truck.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond-quarter%20sales%20of%20the%20Mach-E%20fell%2021%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202022%20(10%2C941%20vehicles)%20to%20the%20same%20period%20this%20year%20(8%2C633).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErich%20Merkle%2C%20Ford's%20head%20of%20US%20sales%20analysis%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20Ford's%20EV%20sales%20overall%20were%20up%20nearly%2012%25%20through%20June.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20all%20of%20the%20unsold%20Mach-E%20inventory%20isn't%20just%20sitting%20on%20dealer%20lots%2C%20because%20it%20spends%20more%20time%20in%20transit.%20About%2052%25%20of%20undelivered%20Mach-Es%20are%20still%20in%20transit%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeliveries%20of%20the%20Lighting%20are%20also%20up%20this%20year%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20when%20production%20of%20the%20vehicle%20was%20still%20ramping%20up%2C%20but%20the%20rate%20of%20sales%20appears%20to%20be%20slowing%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Cloud%20Theory.%20They%20say%20the%20automaker%20sold%2070%25%20of%20its%20Lightning%20inventory%20within%2030%20days%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20last%20year%2C%20but%20has%20only%20been%20able%20to%20sell%2039.3%25%20of%20it%20within%20that%20time%20frame%20so%20far%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord's%20targeting%20EV%20production%20of%20600%2C000%20vehicles%20this%20year.%20But%20while%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Fford-run-ev-ice-businesses-separately-2022-03-02%2F%5C%22%3Eplows%20%2450%20billion%20into%20the%20new%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20expecting%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-losing-billions-on-electric-vehicles-evs-2023-3%5C%22%3Elose%20at%20least%20%243%20billion%20in%20the%20process%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20likely%20won't%20turn%20a%20profit%20on%20the%20segment%20for%20three%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.carscoops.com%2F2023%2F05%2Fford-is-losing-almost-60000-for-every-ev-it-sells%2F%5C%22%3Eit's%20losing%20about%20%2458%2C000%20on%20each%20EV%20it%20sells%3C%2Fa%3E%20(not%20abnormal%20for%20the%20first%20few%20years%20of%20a%20launch.)%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffordauthority.com%2F2023%2F06%2F2023-ford-mustang-mach-e-eligible-for-3k-inventory-discount%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHefty%20rebates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-mustang-mach-e-price-cuts-tesla-price-war-electric-cars-evs-2023-1%5C%22%3Esteep%20price%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20Tesla's%20price%20war%20aren't%20helping%20profitability%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20required%20dealers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2022%2F09%2F14%2Fford-outlines-ev-investment-structure-for-its-dealers-as-it-chases-tesla-like-profit.html%5C%22%3Espend%20anywhere%20from%20%24500%2C000%20to%20over%20%241%20million%20to%20become%20%26quot%3BEV%20certified%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sell%20the%20expensive%20and%20usually%20unprofitable%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat's%20turning%20some%20dealers%20away%20from%20EVs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20East%20Coast%20Ford%20dealer%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20they're%20bullish%20about%20and%20invested%20in%20EVs%2C%20Ford's%20current%20production%20rate%20is%20out%20of%20step%20with%20customer%20demand.%20(The%20dealer%20spoke%20with%20Insider%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20out%20of%20concern%20for%20professional%20repercussions.%20Their%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Insider.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Ford's%20got%20a%20real%20problem%20on%20their%20hands%20based%20on%20the%20bets%20they've%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20Lightnings%20in%20stock%20and%20Mach-Es%20in%20stock.%20We've%20never%20had%20that%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20dealers%20are%20given%20monthly%20allocations%20from%20Ford's%20assembly%20plants%20based%20on%20dealer%20needs%20and%20specific%20market%20demands.%20EV%20allocation%20has%20been%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20for%20some%20Ford%20dealers%2C%20who%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.autonews.com%2Fdealers%2F29-ford-dealers-leave-ev-program-after-changes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclaimed%20in%20lawsuits%20that%20Ford's%20EV%20sales%20requirements%20violate%20franchise%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20production%20is%20exceeding%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20East%20Coast%20dealer%20added.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20able%20to%20decline%20allocation%E2%80%A6%20We%20didn't%20decline%20any%20model%20except%20EVs.%26quot%3B%20They%20noted%2C%20anecdotally%2C%20other%20Ford%20dealers%20that%20they%20speak%20with%20have%20declined%20some%20of%20their%20Mach-E%20allocation%20from%20Ford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMerkle%2C%20of%20Ford%2C%20was%20not%20able%20to%20immediately%20confirm%20whether%20dealers%20were%20turning%20away%20Mach-E%20allocations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20EV%20market%20is%20having%20its%20first%20growing%20pains%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20its%20struggle%20to%20match%20EV%20production%20with%20demand.%20Even%20Tesla%2C%20the%20world's%20top%20seller%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20has%20had%20trouble%20with%20bloated%20inventory%20this%20year%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20series%20of%20price%20reductions%20and%20deals%20on%20Supercharger%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERival%20GM%2C%20which%20is%20also%20investing%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20electrification%2C%20also%20has%20very%20low%20electric%20vehicle%20sales%20numbers.%20Through%20June%2C%20GM%20had%20sold%202%2C316%20Cadillac%20Lyriq%20EVs%20and%2049%20Hummer%20EVs.%20For%20Hummer%2C%20that's%20compared%20to%20371%20deliveries%20in%20the%20same%20period%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20all%20a%20reflection%20of%20how%20difficult%20the%20next%20five%20or%20ten%20years%20will%20be%20for%20EVs%20now%20that%20the%20industry%20has%20surpassed%20the%20early-adopter%20market%2C%20industry%20analysts%20say.%20As%20the%20US%20car%20industry%20nears%20EV%20sales%20totaling%2010%25%20of%20the%20market%2C%20a%20plateau%20is%20appearing%2C%20Karl%20Brauer%2C%20an%20executive%20analyst%20for%20iSeeCars%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20seems%20to%20be%20this%20natural%20resistance%20somewhere%20between%207%25%20and%2010%25%20of%20market%20share%20in%20a%20given%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Brauer%20said%2C%20citing%20a%20recent%20iSeeCars%20study%20that%20found%20the%20states%20with%20the%20biggest%20EV%20sales%20are%20also%20the%20slowest%20growing.%20%26quot%3BThat%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20cap%2C%20and%20then%20it%20gets%20much%20harder%20to%20grow%20it%20further.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELightning%20orders%20still%20not%20getting%20filled%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20Lightning%2C%20Ford%20said%20it%20received%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kbb.com%2Fcar-news%2Fford-closes-reservations-for-f-150-lightning-has-3-year-backlog%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFord%2520s