ing%20the%20different%20vibes%20people%20bring%20to%20their%20Airbnbs%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D7aa9b44fd0ba7a63f76f76d7b5509e20e5b00b98734195ee6ba65e367ed74c39%26postID%3D64ad714c823b1533d1be4cdb%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.airbnb.com%252Frooms%252F49717924%253Fsource_impression_id%253Dp3_1682296974_JExtSoisFHVoeTDL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereally%20great%20experience%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20host%20at%20an%20Airbnb%20in%20Italy.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20that%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rented%20out%20my%20house%20in%20Tennessee%20to%20some%20students%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Iceland%2C%20but%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20get%20into%20the%20short-term-rental%20space.%20Last%20summer%20we%20sold%20that%20long-term%20rental%20and%20bought%20a%20condo%20in%20the%20Orlando%20area%20to%20rent%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20learned%20a%20lot%20of%20lessons%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-ice-age-higher-home-prices-fewer-sales-inventory-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20market%20is%20unpredictable%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20cleaner%20makes%20or%20breaks%20your%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sold%20the%20Orlando%20apartment%20in%20December%20because%20we%20were%20only%20making%20around%20%24100%20in%20profit%20each%20month.%20It%20was%20going%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20liability%20if%20we%20kept%20it%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20cut%20our%20losses%20and%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThen%20I%20saw%20a%20post%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F442411303158530%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3EFacebook%20group%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20from%20an%20investor%20who%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20cohost%20to%20help%20him%20manage%20his%20Airbnbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20anything%20about%20cohosting%2C%20but%20I%20was%20interested%20in%20learning.%20I'd%20been%20toying%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20helping%20others%20manage%20their%20property%20for%20a%20while%20using%20the%20techniques%20and%20systems%20I'd%20learned%20and%20built%20with%20our%20Florida%20condo.%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investor%20has%20Airbnbs%20units%20across%20the%20US.%20He%20wanted%20someone%20to%20help%20run%20his%20apartments%20and%20manage%20the%20guest%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20video%20chat%20with%20him.%20He%20really%20liked%20me%2C%20and%20we%20did%20the%20digital%20version%20of%20an%20old-fashioned%20handshake.%20We%20started%20cohosting%20three%20of%20his%20apartment%20units%20in%20September.%20We%20added%20a%20fourth%20in%20December%20and%20a%20fifth%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20charge%20a%20market%20rate%20of%2020%25%20of%20his%20gross%20revenue%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20managing%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20short-term%20rental%2C%20but%20we%20can%20customize%20our%20pricing%20based%20on%20the%20owner's%20needs.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20charge%2015%25%20for%20guest%20and%20cleaner%20communication%2C%20pricing%20strategy%2C%20and%20listing%20updates.%20For%20guest%20and%20cleaning-team%20communication%20only%2C%20we%20charge%207.5%25.%20Setting%20up%20a%20new%20listing%20is%20a%20one-time%20fee%20of%20%2450.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20making%20way%20more%20cohosting%20than%20we%20did%20as%20hosts%20ourselves.%20The%20investor%20loves%20it%20because%20he's%20able%20to%20step%20back%20and%20focus%20on%20other%20parts%20of%20his%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20look%20after%20communications%2C%20he%20handles%20anything%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20on%20the%20ground.%20Recently%2C%20one%20apartment%20had%20ants%20coming%20into%20the%20kitchen.%20I%20texted%20the%20owner%2C%20and%20he%20went%20over%20with%20traps%20and%20took%20care%20of%20it.%20If%20the%20issue%20is%20in%20a%20city%20the%20owner%20isn't%20in%2C%20he'll%20have%20a%20local%20guy%20sort%20out%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20work%20on%20pricing%20strategies%2C%20where%20we%20set%20the%20prices%20for%20the%20nights%20based%20on%20the%20time%20of%20year%20and%20what%20the%20competition%20is%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20we%20edit%20the%20listings%20to%20boost%20them%20in%20the%20algorithm%2C%20change%20the%20pictures%2C%20and%20create%20the%20copy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20spend%20about%203%20hours%20a%20week%20working%20as%20a%20cohost%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECohosting%20is%20integrated%20into%20the%20Airbnb%20platform%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20it%20really%20easy.%20When%20you%20sign%20up%20as%20a%20cohost%2C%20you%20help%20manage%20the%20listing%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20the%20money%20being%20exchanged.%20I'm%20just%20working%20for%20the%20owner%2C%20and%20he%20pays%20me%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonitoring%20the%20app%20is%20hardly%20any%20work%2C%20since%20it's%20just%20like%20waiting%20for%20a%20text.%20It's%20only%20annoying%20when%20you%20get%20a%20message%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20spends%20around%2015%20minutes%20doing%20it%20per%20week%20when%20I'm%20not%20available%2C%20but%20I%20do%20the%20bulk.%20Sometimes%20I%20just%20need%20to%20send%20a%20quick%20response%20to%20guests%2C%20but%20other%20times%20there's%20an%20issue%20and%20we%20have%20to%20get%20it%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBalancing%20my%20personal%20life%20and%20a%20full-time%20job%20with%20the%20time%20difference%20of%20cohosting%20is%20the%20hardest%20part%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20four%20hours%20ahead%20of%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%201-year-old%2C%20so%20our%20schedule%20is%20already%20kind%20of%20crazy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20the%20app%20set%20up%20to%20go%20through%20my%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20disturb%26quot%3B%20filter%20on%20my%20phone%20so%20I%20can%20hopefully%20get%20woken%20up%20if%20something%20comes%20up%20and%20I'm%20asleep.%20So%20far%20that's%20worked%20fairly%20well%20%E2%80%94%20we%20get%20the%20occasional%20message%20at%202%20a.m.%20our%20time%2C%20but%20not%20many.%20A%20guest%20having%20issues%20at%2010%20p.m.%20their%20time%20is%20the%20most%20challenging%20aspect%20of%20cohosting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20time%20we%20got%20a%20message%20around%202%20a.m.%20our%20time%20and%20I%20slept%20right%20through%20it.%20The%20automatic%20keypad%20had%20stopped%20working%20for%20some%20reason%20and%20our%20guests%20couldn't%20get%20into%20the%20condo.%20I%20woke%20up%20a%20few%20hours%20later%20and%20saw%20all%20the%20messages%20and%20panicked%20a%20bit.%20Thankfully%20a%20security%20guard%20had%20driven%20by%20on%20his%20golf%20cart%2C%20verified%20they%20were%20guests%20in%20the%20condo%2C%20and%20let%20them%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20stuff%20happens%20that's%20out%20of%20your%20control%20and%20you%20have%20to%20just%20roll%20with%20the%20punches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20hear%20of%20crazy%20stories%20like%20parties%2C%20fights%2C%20and%20rude%20guests%2C%20but%20we%20haven't%20really%20had%20any%20of%20those%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20screening%2C%20including%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20guests%20on%20the%20phone%20before%20we%20let%20them%20book%20our%20apartments.%20Sometimes%20guests%20will%20innocuously%20ask%20for%20a%20discount%20or%20for%20an%20early%20check-in%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20time%20those%20will%20be%20problem%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20cohost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fezra-miller-airbnb-iceland-woman-hypnotized-cult-allegations-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan