er%20requested%20their%20vacation%20for%20August%20so%20they'll%20be%20on%20vacation%20whether%20the%20strike%20happens%20or%20not.%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20UPS%20driver%20from%20Ohio%20said%20they%20really%20like%20their%20job%20and%20feel%20lucky%20to%20work%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETheir%20least%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20job%20is%20the%20drama.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20there's%20tension%20and%20friction%20between%20the%20union%20and%20corporate%20side%20of%20UPS.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20UPS%20driver%20in%20Ohio.%20They%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20to%20protect%20their%20job%2C%20but%20their%20employment%20has%20been%20confirmed%20by%20Insider.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20like%20driving%20for%20UPS.%20Even%20though%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20college%20degree%2C%20I%20make%20good%20money%20%E2%80%94%20%2440%20an%20hour.%20I%20don't%20think%20you%20can%20expect%20that%20in%20many%20other%20places%20without%20an%20advanced%20education.%20Some%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fmoney%2Fcareers%2F2022%2F10%2F24%2Fhow-much-do-amazon-drivers-make%2F10350464002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20drivers%20only%20make%20%2421%20an%20hour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20know%20I'm%20lucky%20to%20be%20where%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-a-ups-delivery-driver-what-my-job-is-like-2022-2%5C%22%3EI%20worked%20for%20UPS%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2012%20years%2C%20before%20I%20became%20a%20driver%2C%20and%20I%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity.%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20quit%20my%20other%20jobs%20because%20I'd%20make%20enough%20money%20to%20support%20myself%20and%20my%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAs%20someone%20who's%20been%20on%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20the%20totem%20pole%2C%20I%20get%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20was%20a%20driver%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20preloader%20which%20means%20I%20came%20in%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20loaded%20the%20trucks%20for%20the%20drivers.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20driver%2C%20I%20try%20to%20be%20sympathetic%20toward%20preloaders%20because%20sometimes%20drivers%20can%20get%20really%20frustrated%20with%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20fellow%20drivers%20that%20the%20preloaders%20are%20doing%20their%20best%20and%20we%20should%20be%20kind%20to%20them.%20Everyone's%20just%20trying%20their%20best.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20still%20thinking%20of%20those%20employees%2C%20even%20as%20I've%20moved%20up%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20job%20is%20the%20sense%20of%20independence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20so%20thankful%20that%20I%20can%20be%20handed%20the%20keys%20every%20day%20and%20trusted%20to%20do%20what%20I%20need%20to%20do.%20I%20have%20my%20route%2C%20I%20have%20my%20packages%2C%20and%20I%20know%20how%20to%20do%20my%20job.%20There's%20no%20one%20breathing%20over%20my%20shoulder%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20think%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftruck-driver-trucking-family-2018-6%5C%22%3Elonely%20to%20be%20on%20the%20road%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20eight%20to%2010%20hours%20a%20day%20by%20yourself%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20mind%20it%20and%20I've%20made%20connections%20with%20the%20people%20along%20my%20route.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe're%20called%20service%20providers%20and%20I%20take%20that%20seriously%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20people%20moving%20in%20and%20out%20of%20houses%20all%20the%20time%2C%20I%20try%20to%20welcome%20new%20people%20to%20the%20neighborhood%20and%20get%20to%20know%20them%20a%20little.%20You%20start%20to%20anticipate%20their%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20know%20who%20orders%20packages%20online%20frequently%20and%20who%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20quiet.%20I'm%20providing%20a%20service%20and%20I%20want%20to%20meet%20my%20customers'%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20all%20have%20problem%20children%20on%20our%20route%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20people%20want%20to%20paint%20the%20company%20as%20doing%20something%20wrong%20because%20they%20didn't%20get%20their%20way.%20I%20had%20a%20customer%20who%20had%20a%20case%20of%20wine%20delivered%20a%20couple%20days%20after%20Christmas.%20We%20had%20that%20big%20deep%20freeze%20and%20stuff%20sitting%20in%20trailers%20froze.%20It%20actually%20defrosted%20and%20came%20in%20broken%20so%20people%20blamed%20the%20drivers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20driving%20for%20UPS%20for%2010%20years%20and%20I%20wish%20customers%20would%20understand%20we're%20people%2C%20too.%20I%20know%20so%20many%20things%20are%20automated%20now%20and%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20the%20person%20who%20is%20dropping%20off%20your%20packages%20doesn't%20exist%20outside%20of%20that%20but%20they%20do.%20I%20have%20a%20whole%20life%20%E2%80%94%20being%20a%20UPS%20driver%20is%20just%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20least%20favorite%20part%20of%20working%20at%20UPS%20is%20the%20drama%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20drama%20between%20the%20union%20and%20the%20corporate%20side.%20I%20really%20appreciate%20everything%20the%20union%20does%20for%20us%20and%20the%20benefits%20they've%20secured%2C%20but%20I%20can%20understand%20how%20some%20people%20might%20think%20it's%20too%20strong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20you%20feel%20like%20people%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20union%20when%20they're%20just%20actually%20not%20good%20workers%20and%20shouldn't%20be%20there.%20I%20can%20understand%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20tension%20and%20friction%20this%20year%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20there%20will%20be%20negotiations%20between%20UPS%20and%20Teamsters%2C%20the%20union%20that%20represents%20the%20company's%20340%2C000%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-teamsters-contract-negotiations-issues-pay-massive-strike-looming-2023-7%5C%22%3Edrivers%20and%20package%20handlers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-ceo-carol-tome-compromise-drivers-teamsters-threaten-strike-2023-1%5C%22%3Ecurrent%20contract%20expires%20on%20July%2031%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20if%20an%20agreement%20isn't%20reached%20for%20a%20new%20contract%2C%20there%20could%20be%20a%20strike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20trying%20to%20think%20ahead%20and%20I've%20decided%20to%20request%20to%20use%20my%20vacation%20time%20to%20take%20place%20in%20August.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20prepared.%20Some%20people%20might%20not%20like%20it%20but%20I'm%20not%20the%20type%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20picket%20line.%20This%20way%2C%20I'll%20be%20on%20vacation%20whether%20the%20strike%20happens%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20UPS%20driver%20with%20an%20interesting%20story%3F%20Contact%20Manseen%20Logan%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22bbc1891321ff71908badb4f98dd7055d%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amlogan%40insider.com%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emlogan%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-driver-loves-job-hates-drama-office-politics-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689152400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad85718ed31300199e74d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fups-driver-loves-job-hates-drama-office-politics-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20UPS%20driver%20enjoys%20his%20job%20but%20doesn't%20like%20the%20tension%20between%20his%20union%20