for%20thousands%20of%20years.%20The%20ancient%20Greek%20philosophers%20Socrates%20and%20Plato%20had%20a%20different%20word%20for%20it%20%E2%80%94%20Akrasia%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20still%20meant%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProcrastinating%20is%20delaying%20or%20postponing%20a%20task%20you%20know%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%20The%20end%20result%20is%20often%20regret%2C%20depression%2C%20and%20self-loathing.%20So%20why%20do%20we%20do%20this%20to%20ourselves%3F%20And%20what%20can%20we%20do%20to%20reverse%20the%20bothersome%20trend%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20we%20procrastinate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20to%20understand%20the%20real%20reasons%20we%20procrastinate%2C%20let's%20debunk%20the%20%231%20myth%20about%20why%20we%20do%20it%20in%20the%20first%20place%3A%20Because%20we're%20disorganized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENot%20true%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BProcrastination%20is%20not%20a%20time%20management%20issue.%20It's%20an%20emotional%20management%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Petr%20Ludwig%2C%20author%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famzn.to%2F3XuGsWL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20End%20of%20Procrastination%3A%20How%20to%20Stop%20Postponing%20and%20Lead%20a%20Fulfilled%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20we%20procrastinate%20because%20of%20how%20we%20feel%20about%20the%20task%2C%20not%20because%20we're%20bad%20at%20making%20to-do%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwriteaboutnowmedia.com%2Fpodcast%2F2023%2F6%2F20%2Fhow-to-stop-procrastination-and-get-things-done%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20interview%20on%20the%20Write%20About%20Now%20Podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ludwig%20shared%20his%20science-backed%20insights%20on%20why%20we%20procrastinate%20and%20the%20helpful%20tools%20we%20use%20to%20combat%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argues%20that%20the%20real%20reasons%20we%20put%20things%20off%20are%20a%20lack%20of%20intrinsic%20motivation%2C%20willpower%2C%20and%20fear%20of%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Lack%20of%20motivation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20feel%20a%20lack%20of%20purpose%20at%20work.%20In%20a%20post-pandemic%20world%20amidst%20a%20global%20economic%20crisis%20and%20political%20turmoil%2C%20feeling%20inspired%20about%20the%20world%20can%20be%20challenging%20%E2%80%94%20much%20less%20your%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20motivated%20at%20work%20because%20we%20don't%20believe%20in%20what%20we%20are%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Ludwig.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20working%20on%20a%20project%20and%20you%20lack%20purpose%2C%20it's%20truly%20difficult%20to%20stay%20motivated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20escaping%20from%20the%20stress%20and%20effort%20of%20a%20particular%20task%20by%20doing%20something%20you%20know%20you%20shouldn't%20do.%20As%20the%20great%20American%20writer%20Mark%20Twain%20once%20joked%2C%20%26quot%3BNever%20put%20off%20till%20tomorrow%20what%20may%20be%20done%20the%20day%20after%20tomorrow%20just%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Fear%20of%20failure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20we%20procrastinate%20is%20because%20we're%20anxious%2C%20often%20irrationally%2C%20that%20the%20result%20of%20our%20work%20might%20not%20be%20well%20received.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20often%20so%20scared%20of%20failure%20that%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ludwig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Lack%20of%20willpower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20faced%20with%20big%20demands%20or%20stressful%20situations%2C%20our%20willpower%20often%20diminishes%2C%20making%20it%20more%20challenging%20to%20resist%20the%20lure%20of%20social%20media%2C%20video%20games%2C%20and%20other%20procrastination%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20stop%20procrastination%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Rekindle%20your%20purpose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20noted%20earlier%2C%20procrastination%20points%20to%20a%20larger%20problem%20that%20you%20lack%20overall%20purpose%20in%20your%20life%2C%20so%20it%20may%20be%20time%20to%20get%20it%20back.%20Ludwig%20encourages%20you%20to%20think%20about%20the%20activities%20that%20you%20truly%20enjoy%20doing%20in%20your%20life%20and%20the%20tasks%20that%20make%20you%20feel%20the%20most%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20work%2C%20ask%20yourself%20what%20your%20strengths%20are%20and%20how%20you%20can%20deploy%20those%20strengths%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20advises.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20small%20steps%20that%20can%20improve%20your%20daily%20life%20because%20the%20more%20intrinsic%20motivation%20you%20have%2C%20the%20more%20often%20you%20are%20in%20what%20is%20called%20a%20state%20of%20flow.%20You%20enjoy%20the%20process.%20Time%20stops%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20state%20of%20flow%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20the%20exact%20opposite%20of%20procrastination%20because%20when%20you're%20doing%20something%20meaningful%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20positive%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Enjoy%20the%20path%2C%20not%20the%20destination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELudwig%20encourages%20people%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20the%20journey%20than%20the%20end%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20is%20the%20best%20solution%20for%20fighting%20procrastination%20because%20when%20you%20enjoy%20the%20process%2C%20you%20love%20what%20you%20are%20doing%20and%20won't%20postpone%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Break%20big%20tasks%20into%20smaller%20tasks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20just%20the%20overwhelming%20nature%20of%20a%20task%20you%20dread%20doing%20can%20be%20paralyzing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOvercoming%20this%20paralysis%20often%20involves%20breaking%20down%20the%20task%20into%20smaller%2C%20more%20manageable%20steps%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20less%20overwhelming%20and%20more%20attainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20Ludwig%20describes%20as%20emotional%20management.%20%26quot%3BYour%20very%20intense%20negative%20emotion%20towards%20the%20task%20goes%20down%2C%20and%20your%20willpower%20kicks%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ludwig.%20%26quot%3BStronger%20willpower%20also%20leads%20to%20greater%20satisfaction%20because%20when%20we%20manage%20to%20prioritize%20better%2C%20the%20centers%20of%20rewards%20in%20our%20brains%20are%20activated%2C%20dopamine%20is%20released%2C%20and%20we%20experience%20positive%20emotions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Cut%20yourself%20some%20slack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%20you%20catch%20yourself%20procrastinating%2C%20practice%20a%20little%20compassion%20instead%20of%20beating%20yourself%20up%20about%20it.%20%26quot%3BSelf-forgiveness%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20helpful%20strategy%20in%20fighting%20procrastination%2C%20says%20Ludwig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20points%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0191886910000474%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20done%20at%20Carlton%20University%20in%202009%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20119%20first-year%20students%20were%20asked%20to%20complete%20measures%20of%20procrastination%20and%20self-forgiveness%20immediately%20before%20two%20midterm%20exams.%20Results%20revealed%20that%20the%20students%20who%20forgave%20themselves%20for%20procrastinating%20in%20prepping%20for%20the%20first%20exam%20were%20less%20likely%20to%20procrastinate%20in%20studying%20for%20the%20second%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it's%20just%20about%20forgiving%20ourselves%20and%20starting%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Ludwig%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Small%20is%20editor-in-chief%20of%20%26quot%3BGreen%20Entrepreneur%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20vertical%20from%20Entrepreneur%20Media%20focused%20on%20the%20intersection%20of%20sustainability%20and%20business.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-overcome-procrastination-expert-strategies-conquer-emotional-issue-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689152400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64adb6fe8ed31300199e82c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-overcome-procrastination-expert-strategies-conquer-emotional-issue-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Author%20Petr%20Ludwig%20says%20procrastination%20happens%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20intrinsic%20motivation%2C%20willpower%2C%20and%20fear%20of%20failure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jonathan%20Small)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-overcome-procrastination-expert-strategies-conquer-emotional-issue-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20bought%20Frontier's%20%241%2C999%20all-you-can-fly%20pass%20for%20%24599.%20I%20wish%20I%20knew%20about%20these%203%20big%20downsides%2C%20but%20I'll%20still%20be%20saving%20money.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222376%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joshua%20Holi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ae4b8f94be880019f38640%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221782%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoshua%20Holi%20is%20a%20product%20manager%20who%20bought%20the%20Frontier%20Airlines%20%26quot%3BGo%20Wild%26quot%3Bpass.%20It%20might%20not%20be%20a%20great%20deal%20for%20everyone%2C%20though.%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Holi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrontier%20Airlines%20now%20offers%20an%20all%20you%20can%20fly%20pass%20but%20there%20are%20some%20catches.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20only%20book%20flights%2024%20hours%20in%20advance%20for%20domestic%20travel%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20be%20a%20spontaneous%20flier.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20also%20have%20to%20pay%20extra%20money%20on%20top%20of%20the%20pass%20for%20your%20carry-ons%20and%20checked%20bags.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40know_vember%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoshua%20Holi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20product%20manager%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20Pennsylvania.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20five%20years%20I've%20flown%20with%20American%20Airlines%2C%20but%20when%20Frontier%20began%20offering%20an%20all-you-can-fly%20pass%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20jump%20at%20the%20opportunity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pass%20is%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyfrontier.com%2Fdeals%2Fgowild-pass%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoWild%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20it%20allows%20passengers%20the%20chance%20to%20hop%20on%20any%20domestic%20or%20international%20Frontier%20flight.%20I%20bought%20the%20%241%2C999%20annual%20pass%20for%20%24600%20during%20a%20limited-time%2048-hour%20sale.%20While%20it%20may%20seem%20great%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwsj-frontiers-1999-all-you-can-fly-pass-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethere%20are%20some%20caveats%20you%20should%20be%20aware%20of%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20pass%20doesn't%20last%20forever.%20If%20you%20don't%20cancel%20after%20the%20first%20year%2C%20the%20pass%20will%20renew%20automatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20about%20the%20%24600%20deal%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20savings%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20original%20retail%20price.%20I'm%20a%20product%20manager%20who%20travels%20throughout%20the%20US%20for%20work%2C%20so%20I%20bought%20the%20pass%20knowing%20I%20could%20get%20my%20money%20back%20rather%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20saw%20the%20pass%20as%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20personal%20travel%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20I%20love%20traveling%20to%20Florida%2C%20and%20I'm%20eager%20to%20go%20to%20Puerto%20Rico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20are%20three%20things%20I%20wish%20I%20knew%20before%20buying%20my%20pass%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Long%20layovers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20purchasing%20my%20pass%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20would%20have%20paid%20attention%20to%20the%20layovers.%20After%20doing%20some%20research%20I%20noticed%20most%20flights%20with%20Frontier%20have%20very%20long%20layovers.%20I've%20seen%20some%20stops%20that%20are%20over%2020%20hours%20long.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20book%20a%20flight%20from%20Philadelphia%20to%20San%20Diego%2C%20but%20the%20shortest%20layover%20was%2012%20hours%2C%20which%20might%20not%20be%20a%20possibility%20for%20those%20who%20need%20to%20make%20a%20quick%20trip%20and%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layovers%20were%20a%20huge%20surprise%20to%20me%20personally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Short%20timeframe%20for%20booking%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20you%20have%20to%20book%20the%20flight%2024%20hours%20before%20you%20plan%20to%20depart%20for%20domestic%20travel%20and%2010%20days%20before%20international%20travel.%20This%20means%20you%20need%20to%20be%20a%20spontaneous%20flier%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20book%20your%20trip%20to%20another%20US%20city%20a%20month%20in%20advance%2C%20or%20even%20two%20days%20before%20your%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20might%20be%20okay%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20visit%20family%20and%20have%20a%20guaranteed%20place%20to%20stay%2C%20but%20it%20might%20not%20be%20the%20best%20option%20if%20you're%20someone%20who%20needs%20to%20plan%20your%20trips%20well%20in%20advance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20means%20you%20can't%20book%20a%20round%20trip.%20Instead%2C%20using%20your%20pass%20you%20can%20book%20your%20trip%20to%20your%20destination%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20book%20your%20flight%20home%20due%20to%20the%2024%20hour%20rule%20for%20domestic%20flights.%20You%20have%20two%20options%20in%20this%20case%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBook%20your%20flight%20home%2024%20hours%20before%20you%20need%20to%20return%20(which%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20more%20risky%20because%20there%20might%20not%20be%20a%20flight%20home%20on%20your%20desired%20date)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBook%20a%20normal%20flight%20home%20without%20using%20the%20GoWild%20pass%2C%20knowing%20the%20flight%20will%20be%20more%20costly%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Additional%20fees%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20to%20consider%20is%20the%20extra%20fees%20%E2%80%94%20you%20still%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20your%20baggage.%20This%20means%20you%20have%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flyfrontier.com%2Ftravel%2Ftravel-info%2Fbag-options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20a%20carry-on%20bag%20fee%2C%20and%20a%20checked%20baggage%20fee%2C%20too.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20cost%20for%20your%20bags%20will%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20date%20of%20your%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20also%20have%20to%20pay%20taxes%20for%20that%20flight.%20The%20taxes%20you%20pay%20will%20also%20vary%20per%20flight%20and%20airport.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20often%20%2430.00.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIs%20it%20a%20good%20option%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20this%20pass%20seems%20to%20be%20well-suited%20for%20remote%20workers%20who%20have%20flexible%20work%20schedules%2C%20or%20for%20people%20who%20like%20to%20travel%20and%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20work%20from%20different%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20if%20you're%20someone%20who%20has%20to%20head%20into%20the%20office%20everyday%20or%20who%20can't%20pack%20up%20and%20leave%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20the%20best%20choice%20for%20you.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20purchasing%20this%20pass%2C%20I%20recommend%20doing%20some%20research%20on%20the%20airline%20and%20its%20routes.%20While%20it%20might%20be%20great%20for%20spontaneous%20travelers%20who%20fly%20often%2C%20it's%20certainly%20not%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20travel%20hack%20and%20would%20like%20to%20share%20your%20story%2C%20email%20Alyshia%20Hull%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aahull%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eahull%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-frontiers-all-you-can-fly-gowild-pass-downsides-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689152400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64538530b4a8cd00187ab58d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-frontiers-all-you-can-fly-gowild-pass-downsides-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joshua%20Holi%20is%20a%20frequent%20traveler%20who%20purchased%20Frontier%20Airlines'%20new%20%26quot%3Ball-you-can-fly%26quot%3B%20GoWild%20Pass.%20He%20says%20there%20are%203%20big%20caveats%20to%20the%20pass.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alyshia%20Hull)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-frontiers-all-you-can-fly-gowild-pass-downsides-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Chandrayaan%20Whodunnit%20To%20Propel%20ISRO's%20Next%20Moonshot%20Friday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20lessons%20learnt%20four%20years%20ago%20and%20equipped%20with%20more%20fuel%20and%20fortified%20safety%20measures%2C%20India's%20third%20lunar%20mission%2C%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20ready%20to%20make%20its%20leap%20towards%20the%20moon%20on%20Friday%20at%202%3A35%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20as%20a%20follow-up%20mission%20after%20the%20hard%20landing%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%20in%20September%202019%20due%20to%20a%20software%20and%20hardware%20anomaly.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20ISRO%20Chairman%20S%20Somanath%20revealed%20how%20the%20space%20agency%20has%20learned%20from%20past%20failures%20and%20implemented%20changes%20for%20the%20upcoming%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20lacuna%20in%20the%20last%20Chandrayaa-2%20mission%20was%20that%20there%20were%20off-nominal%20conditions%20that%20were%20initiated%20in%20the%20system.%20Everything%20was%20not%20nominal.%20And%20the%20craft%20was%20not%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20off-nominal%20condition%20for%20a%20safe%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanath%20explained%20that%20the%20new%20mission%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20land%20successfully%20even%20if%20certain%20elements%20fail.%20Several%20scenarios%20including%20sensor%20failure%2C%20engine%20failure%2C%20algorithm%20failure%2C%20and%20calculation%20failure%20were%20examined%20and%20measures%20developed%20to%20counteract%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20essential%20lesson%20is%2C%20in%20any%20space%20mission%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20conditions%20of%20normality.%20So%2C%20how%20we%20address%20them%20and%20how%20we%20mitigate%20the%20possibilities%20of%20a%20failure%20in%20such%20an%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20added%20new%20instruments%20to%20handle%20failures%2C%20new%20algorithms%20to%20handle%20off-nominal%20situations%2C%20new%20approaches%20to%20soft%20land%20in%20case%20of%20not-availability%2C%20any%20such%20measurements%20and%20total%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20primary%20issues%20with%20Chandrayaan-2%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20engines%20developing%20higher%20thrust%20than%20expected%2C%20leading%20to%20accumulated%20errors%20and%20fast%20turns%20that%20exceeded%20the%20software's%20expected%20rates.%20The%20500m%20x%20500m%20landing%20site%20also%20proved%20too%20small%20for%20the%20spacecraft's%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20has%20been%20designed%20with%20these%20issues%20in%20mind%2C%20expanding%20the%20landing%20area%20to%204%20km%20by%202.5%20km.%20The%20spacecraft%20also%20carries%20more%20fuel%20and%20additional%20solar%20panels%20to%20ensure%20power%20generation%20regardless%20of%20its%20landing%20orientation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20strengthened%20the%20lander%20in%20various%20ways%2C%20like%20increasing%20the%20propellant%20loading%20in%20the%20lander...%20added%20more%20of%20solar%20power%20generation%20capability...%20as%20to%20have%20more%20tolerance%20to%20non-orientation%20or%20wrong%20orientation%20of%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20added%20new%20sensors%20like%20the%20laser%20Doppler%20velocity%20emitter%20to%20handle%20or%20to%20measure%20the%20velocity%20of%20the%20craft%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20and%20have%20redundancies%20of%20measurements%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20already%20existing%20optical%20measurements%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLegs%20of%20the%20lander%2C%20though%20that's%20configuration%20remains%20the%20same%2C%20structurally%20it%20has%20been%20strengthened%20to%20handle%20almost%20one%20meter%20per%20second%20additional%20velocity%20also.%20So%2C%20that%20even%20if%20it%20has%20a%20hard%20landing%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20survival%20could%20be%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISRO%20chief%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20has%20also%20conducted%20a%2024-hour%20%26quot%3Blaunch%20rehearsal%26quot%3B%20simulating%20the%20entire%20launch%20preparation%20and%20process%20for%20the%20upcoming%20mission.%20Chandrayaan-3%20will%20launch%20aboard%20a%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark%203%20(LVM3)%20from%20the%20spaceport%20at%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mission's%20objectives%20include%20demonstrating%20safe%20landing%20and%20roving%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%2C%20developing%20new%20technologies%20for%20inter-planetary%20missions%2C%20and%20continuing%20the%20scientific%20investigations%20initiated%20by%20previous%20missions.%20The%20orbiter%20from%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%20still%20in%20good%20health%2C%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20relay%20station%20for%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20will%20target%20a%20similar%20landing%20site%20as%20its%20predecessor%2C%20close%20to%20the%20moon's%20South%20Pole.%20This%20region%20is%20of%20interest%20due%20to%20the%20potential%20presence%20of%20water%20discovered%20by%20Chandrayaan-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setback%20with%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20the%20upcoming%20mission.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20space%20agency%20had%20consulted%20experts%2C%20including%20those%20from%20the%20NASA's%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%20(JPL)%20in%20California%20and%20Indian%20Academy%20and%20institutions%2C%20to%20ensure%20the%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20brought%20in%20domain%20specialist%20and%20propulsion%2C%20control%20guide%20and%20electronic%20sensors%20and%20various%20flight%20mechanics%2C%20mathematics%2C%20and%20they%20sit%20together%20and%20review%20in%20hundreds%20of%20committees%20and%20reviews%20and%20everywhere%20there%20will%20be%20some%20suggestions%20and%20improvements%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somnath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689152100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fabpc33vc_chandrayaan-pti_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-chandrayaan-whodunnit-to-propel-isros-next-moonshot-friday-4199959%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ISRO%20Chief%20S%20Somanath%20explained%20that%20the%20new%20mission%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20land%20successfully%20even%20if%20certain%20elements%20fail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-chandrayaan-whodunnit-to-propel-isros-next-moonshot-friday-4199959%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-chandrayaan-whodunnit-to-propel-isros-next-moonshot-friday-4199959%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-chandrayaan-whodunnit-to-propel-isros-next-moonshot-friday-4199959%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jay%20Shah%20To%20Visit%20Pakistan%20For%20Asia%20Cup%3F%20BCCI%20Official%20Reacts%20To%20Rumours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20seem%20to%20be%20conflicting%20interests%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20schedule%20and%20venue%20within%20Pakistan.%20While%20the%20'hybrid%20model'%20was%20already%20agreed%20upon%20by%20Najam%20Sethi%2C%20the%20former%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20Chief'%20and%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20the%20Sports%20Minister%20Of%20Pakistan%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page%20as%20the%20nation's%20cricketing%20body.%20As%20varied%20reports%20over%20Pakistan's%20stance%20on%20India's%20decision%20to%20not%20visit%20the%20country%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20forthcoming%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%20continue%2C%20a%20wayward%20rumour%20emerged%20suggesting%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20has%20agreed%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rumours%20spread%20like%20wildfire%2C%20with%20reporters%20from%20Pakistan%20confirming%20the%20development.%20A%20few%20reporters%20even%20claimed%2