Them%20From...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20tomato%20rates%20in%20the%20country%20cross%20new%20milestones%20every%20day%2C%20hovering%20around%20the%20100-rupee%20mark%20for%20weeks%20now%2C%20the%20central%20government%20today%20announced%20steps%20to%20check%20the%20kitchen%20staple's%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%20has%20asked%20National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20and%20National%20Cooperative%20Consumers%20Federation%20to%20procure%20tomatoes%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Maharashtra%20and%20distribute%20them%20in%20areas%20that%20have%20recorded%20the%20biggest%20jump%20in%20tomato%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20stocks%2C%20a%20government%20statement%20said%2C%20will%20be%20available%20to%20consumers%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20at%20discounted%20prices%20by%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centres%20where%20these%20fresh%20stocks%20will%20be%20released%20have%20been%20identified%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20absolute%20hike%20in%20retail%20prices%20over%20the%20past%20one%20month%2C%20the%20government%20said.%20The%20scale%20of%20consumption%20has%20also%20been%20considered%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20tomato%20is%20produced%20in%20nearly%20every%20Indian%20state%2C%20the%20southern%20and%20western%20regions%20account%20for%20nearly%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20country's%20total%20production.%20Their%20surplus%20produce%20is%20then%20used%20to%20ensure%20continuous%20supply%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20production%20seasons%20are%20also%20different%20across%20regions.%20The%20peak%20harvesting%20season%20occurs%20from%20December%20to%20February.%20The%20periods%20during%20July-August%20and%20October-November%20are%20generally%20the%20lean%20production%20months%20for%20tomato%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20price%20hike%20during%20this%20period%2C%20the%20statement%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BJuly%20coinciding%20with%20monsoon%20season%2C%20adds%20to%20further%20challenges%20related%20to%20distribution%20and%20increased%20transit%20losses%20adding%20to%20price%20rise.%20The%20cycle%20of%20planting%20and%20harvesting%20seasons%20and%20variation%20across%20regions%20are%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20price%20seasonality%20in%20Tomato.%20Apart%20from%20the%20normal%20price%20seasonality%2C%20temporary%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20and%20crop%20damage%20due%20to%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%20etc.%20often%20lead%20to%20sudden%20spikes%20in%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20tomato%20supplies%20are%20currently%20coming%20in%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Delhi%20and%20nearby%20cities%20are%20receiving%20stocks%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20from%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20crop%20arrivals%20are%20expected%20soon%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20arrivals%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20start.%20%26quot%3BPrices%20are%20anticipated%20to%20cool%20down%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689151620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqe9u7bvg_tomato_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftomato-prices-tomato-price-hike-delhi-may-get-cheaper-tomatoes-this-weekend-heres-how-4199909%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20tomato%20rates%20in%20the%20country%20cross%20new%20milestones%20every%20day%2C%20hovering%20above%20the%20100-rupee%20mark%20for%20weeks%20now%2C%20the%20central%20government%20today%20announced%20steps%20to%20check%20the%20kitchen%20staple's%20price.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftomato-prices-tomato-price-hike-delhi-may-get-cheaper-tomatoes