2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fpolice-chargesheet-photos-show-brij-bhushan-making-advances-cdrs-match-location-in-testimony-8828323%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20particular%20photographs%2C%20his%20phone%20location%2C%20and%20another%20set%20of%20pictures%20are%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20pieced%20together%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20Singh%20made%20by%20six%20wrestlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20notes%20that%20Singh%20is%20%E2%80%9Cliable%20to%20be%20prosecuted%20and%20punished%20for%20offences%E2%80%9D%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20molestation%2C%20and%20stalking%20under%20Sections%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%2C%20354%20(outraging%20modesty%20of%20a%20woman)%2C%20354%20A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20and%20354%20D%20(stalking)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20highlights%20that%20there%20was%20neither%20a%20Visitor%E2%80%99s%20Register%20nor%20any%20CCTV%20at%20the%20WFI%20office%20on%20Ashoka%20Road%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20and%20the%20scene%20of%20at%20least%20two%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20as%20per%20the%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20police%20notice%2C%20WFI%20officials%20supplied%20four%20photographs%2C%20showing%20the%20presence%20of%20Brij%20Bhushan%20and%20the%20complainant%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20(Kazakhstan)%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20two%20photographs%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20making%20advances%20towards%20the%20complainant%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20records%2015%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20Singh%2C%20and%20the%20police%20have%20so%20far%20examined%20108%20witnesses%20during%20the%20probe.%20Among%20the%20witnesses%20were%20WFI%20officials%2C%20coaches%2C%20referees%2C%20and%20fellow%20participants%20of%20the%20wrestling%20events%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fwrestling-body-chief-brij-bhushan-sharan-singh-liable-prosecuted-punished-delhi-police-chargesheet-2405090-2023-07-11%3Fonetap%3Dtrue%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chargesheet%20noted%20that%20out%20of%20the%20total%20witnesses%2C%2015%20of%20them%20have%20confirmed%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20Singh.%20These%20include%20Vinesh%20Phogat%2C%20Sakshi%20Mallik%2C%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20wrestlers%2C%20including%20a%20minor%2C%20had%20filed%20separate%20complaints%20with%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Connaught%20Place%20police%20station%20against%20Singh%20regarding%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%20on%20April%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20and%20evidence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20complainant%20wrestlers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20(a%20medal)%2C%20the%20coaches%20took%20me%20along%20to%20meet%20Brij%20Bhushan.%20There%20he%20tried%20to%20forcibly%20hug%20me.%20I%20had%20a%20flag%20in%20one%20hand%2C%20so%20I%20tried%20to%20push%20him%20away%20with%20my%20other%20hand%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20relent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9C(Once)%2C%20I%20lost%20a%20bout%20in%20the%20wrestling%20league.%20As%20soon%20as%20I%20moved%20from%20the%20mat%20to%20my%20team%20box%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20headed%20towards%20me%20and%20hugged%20me%20forcibly.%20He%20held%20me%20for%2015-20%20seconds%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20push%20him%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20me%20go.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20two%20photographs%2C%20which%20show%20him%20making%20advances%20towards%20the%20complainant.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20technical%20evidence%2C%20available%20in%20the%20form%20of%20photographs%20and%20videographs%20of%20the%20various%20events%2C%20clearly%20supports%20the%20allegation%20levelled%20by%20the%20complainant%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20accused%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chargesheet%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20complainant%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20called%20in%20the%20WFI%20office%20where%20I%20went%20along%20with%20my%20coach%E2%80%A6%20Bhushan%2C%20who%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20chair%2C%20asked%20me%20to%20sit%20down%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20informed%20him%20about%20my%20injury%20%E2%80%A6%20He%20assured%20me%20of%20all%20the%20help%2C%20but%20asked%20me%20to%20get%20into%20a%20physical%20relationship%20with%20him%20for%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20allegation%20of%20the%20second%20complainant%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20says%20there%20is%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20alleged%20incident%2C%20the%20complainant%E2%80%99s%20coach%20was%20present%20in%20the%20area%20where%20the%20alleged%20meeting%20took%20place.%20The%20coach%E2%80%99s%20mobile%20tower%20location%20was%20in%20the%20area%20of%20North%20Avenue%20near%20the%20vicinity%20of%20Ashoka%20Road%2C%20WFI%20office%20location%2C%20the%20charge%20sheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrestler%20alleged%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20standing%20in%20the%20last%20row%20(for%20team%20photograph)%E2%80%A6%20the%20accused%20(Singh)%20came%20and%20stood%20alongside%20me.%20I%20suddenly%20felt%20a%20hand%20on%20my%20buttock.%20When%20I%20tried%20moving%20away%2C%20I%20was%20forcibly%20held%20by%20my%20shoulder.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20the%20police%20noted%20that%20there%20is%20evidence%20in%20the%20form%20of%20four%20printouts%20of%20coloured%20photographs%20shared%20by%20WFI%20relating%20to%20the%20event.%20In%20these%20photographs%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20said%2C%20the%20complainant%20is%20seen%20sitting%20in%20the%20front%20row%20with%20other%20wrestlers%20and%20these%20photographs%20also%20show%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20was%20also%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20another%20wrestler.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20lying%20down%20on%20the%20mat%2C%20the%20accused%20(Singh)%20came%20near%20me%20and%20to%20my%20shock%20and%20surprise%20leaned%20in%20and%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20my%20coach%2C%20without%20seeking%20my%20permission%20pulled%20up%20my%20T-shirt%2C%20placed%20his%20hand%20on%20my%20breast%20and%20slid%20it%20down%20my%20stomach%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20examining%2Fchecking%20my%20breathing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20my%20visit%20to%20the%20federation%20office%E2%80%A6%20I%20was%20called%20into%20the%20room%20of%20the%20accused%20(Singh)%E2%80%A6%20my%20brother%2C%20who%20was%20accompanying%20me%2C%20was%20categorically%20asked%20to%20stay%20back%E2%80%A6The%20accused%20(Singh)%2C%20upon%20the%20departure%20of%20other%20persons%2C%20closed%20the%20door%E2%80%A6%20pulled%20me%20towards%20himself%20and%20tried%20making%20forceful%20physical%20contact%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evidence%20gathered%20by%20the%20police%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20above%20complainant%E2%80%99s%20allegation%2C%20shows%20the%20complainant%20is%20seen%20standing%20with%20other%20wrestlers%20along%20with%20Singh.%20It%20established%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20the%20complainant%20at%20the%20place%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20charge%20sheet%20notes.%20The%20police%20also%20noted%20that%20WFI%20did%20not%20maintain%20any%20visitor%20register%20at%20the%20office%20and%20no%20CCTV%20camera%20was%20installed%20at%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20wrestler%20alleged%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20pretext%20of%20getting%20a%20picture%20clicked%20with%20me%2C%20he%20pulled%20me%20towards%20him%20by%20my%20shoulder%E2%80%A6%20t