al.%20(...)%20They%20were%20a%20father%20and%20mother%20and%20three%20children.%20(...)%20The%20parents%20and%20children%20were%20adults%2C%20they%20were%20not%20little%20ones%26quot%3B%2C%20Salas%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20Infobae%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20bodies%20have%20been%20airlifted%20to%20Kathmandu%20and%20are%20kept%20at%20Tribhuvan%20University%20Teaching%20Hospital%20for%20post-mortem%2C%20Gyanendra%20Bhul%2C%20Information%20Officer%20at%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20of%20Nepal%20(CAAN)%2C%20The%20Himalayan%20Times%20newspaper%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20in%20Janakpurdham%2C%20Culture%2C%20Tourism%2C%20and%20Civil%20Aviation%20Minister%20Sudan%20Kirati%20announced%20that%20the%20government%20would%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20investigation%20to%20uncover%20the%20factors%20that%20led%20to%20this%20unfortunate%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20passengers%20who%20died%20were%20from%20the%20same%20Mexican%20family%20and%20had%20flown%20to%20the%20Khumbu%20region%20yesterday%20for%20mountain%20flight%20as%20well%20to%20observe%20Sherpa%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Director%20of%20Manang%20Air%2C%20Mukti%20Pandey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENepal's%20tourist%20and%20mountaineering%20season%20ended%20in%20May.%20The%20flights%20carrying%20tourists%20to%20the%20mountains%20are%20less%20common%20this%20time%20of%20year%20as%20visibility%20is%20poor%20and%20weather%20conditions%20fickle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%201997%2C%20Manang%20Air%20is%20a%20helicopter%20airline%20based%20in%20Kathmandu.%20It%20has%20been%20operating%20helicopters%20in%20commercial%20air%20transportation%20within%20the%20Nepalese%20territory%20under%20the%20Regulation%20of%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authority%20of%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20provides%20chartered%20services%20and%20is%20focused%20on%20personalised%20services%20such%20as%20adventure%20