ty%2Fdelhi%2Fanother-horrific-murder-in-delhi-chopped-body-parts-found-near-geeta-colony-flyover%2Farticleshow%2F101690770.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%2F10%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Exam%20Toppers%20From%20One%20Centre%20Sets%20Off%20Vyapam%20Alert%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ghost%20of%20the%20Vyapam%20scam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20infamous%20and%20large-scale%20recruitment%20scandals%20to%20hit%20India%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20returned%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20fresh%20allegations%20of%20large-scale%20examination%20rigging%20clouding%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Employees%20Selection%20Board%20(ESB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Vyapam%2C%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20controversy%20a%20decade%20after%20the%20original%20scandal%20that%20implicated%20several%20high-profile%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20revolves%20around%20the%20recent%20examination%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20Group%202%20and%20Sub%20Group%204%20Patwari%20-%20a%20revenue%20official%2C%20wherein%20seven%20out%20of%20the%20top%20ten%20scorers%20took%20their%20exams%20at%20the%20NRI%20College%2C%20Gwalior.%20This%20exam%20centre%20has%20strong%20links%20to%20BJP%20MLA%20Sanjeev%20Kushwaha%2C%20adding%20a%20political%20layer%20to%20the%20ongoing%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20top%20scorers%20belonged%20to%20a%20minuscule%20fraction%20of%20the%20total%20examinees%2C%20their%20roll%20numbers%20ranging%20from%202488%207991%20to%202488%209693%2C%20from%20a%20pool%20of%20roughly%201%2C700%20candidates.%20Considering%20that%2014%20lakh%20individuals%20took%20the%20exam%2C%20the%20odds%20of%20such%20an%20occurrence%20have%20been%20called%20into%20question%2C%20triggering%20widespread%20speculation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20answer%20sheets%20belonging%20to%20the%20top%2010%20scorers.%20The%20sheets%20reveal%20an%20unusual%20pattern%3A%20candidates%20signed%20their%20exam%20forms%20in%20Hindi%2C%20yet%20answered%20the%20papers%20in%20English.%20These%20candidates%20seemed%20to%20have%20accurately%20answered%20questions%20later%20cancelled%20by%20the%20ESB%2C%20for%20which%20no%20marks%20were%20ultimately%20awarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20examination%20was%20attended%20by%209.78%20lakh%20students%20out%20of%20the%2012.79%20lakh%20applications%20received.%20The%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20June%2030%2C%20with%20the%20list%20of%20the%20top%2010%20candidates%20following%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20Educated%20Youth%20Union%20(NEYU)%20representative%20Ranjit%20Kisanvanshi%20has%20alleged%20that%20exam%20papers%20were%20prematurely%20sold%20by%20brokers%20within%20Vyapam%2C%20bringing%20back%20memories%20of%20the%20original%20scam%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Sanjeev%20Singh%20Kushwaha%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20NRI%20College%20Gwalior%2C%20dismissed%20these%20allegations%2C%20attributing%20them%20to%20political%20motivations%20ahead%20of%20the%20impending%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20former%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20MLA%20Jeetu%20Patwari%20dubbed%20the%20issue%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20chapter%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%20He%20pledged%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20party%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20will%20be%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Staff%20Selection%20Board%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20these%20accusations%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20recent%20developments%20rekindle%20memories%20of%20the%20infamous%20Vyapam%20scam%20that%20erupted%20in%202013%2C%20revealing%20that%20several%20exams%20conducted%20by%20the%20agency%20were%20rigged%20in%20exchange%20for%20money.%20The%20scam%2C%20which%20implicated%20several%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%2