%20written%20by%20Yann%20Phillipin%2C%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20immediately%20known%20what%20the%20Indian%20response%20will%20be.%20Requests%20of%20this%20kind%20are%20usually%20channeled%20through%20the%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20and%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20concerned%20department%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20most%20likely%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DOPT)%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%2C%20which%20look%20after%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Paris%20seeking%20information%20on%20the%20status%20of%20the%20French%20request%20and%20this%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20reply%20is%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Fagustawestland-case-middleman-sushen-gupta-held-classified-papers-of-mod-iaf-and-hal-ed-claims%2Farticleshow%2F69626197.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20currently%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20VVIP%20chopper%20scam.%20Reports%20published%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202021%20exposed%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20deep%20business%20connections%20to%20Dassault%20and%20Thales%20over%20a%2015-year%20period%2C%20which%20allegedly%20involved%20paying%20him%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20million%20euros%20in%20secret%20commissions%20to%20offshore%20accounts%20and%20shell%20companies%E2%80%9D%20using%20inflated%20invoices%20for%20software%20consulting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20explosive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20story%20also%20looks%20at%20another%20part%20of%20the%20Rafale%20puzzle%20%E2%80%93%20the%20tax%20reduction%20Reliance%20Group%20billionaire%20Anil%20Ambani%20secured%20from%20France%20in%202015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reveals%20how%20Ambani%20wrote%20to%20French%20economics%20minister%20(and%20now%20president)%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20finance%20minister%20Michel%20Sapin%2C%20requesting%20their%20personal%20intervention%20to%20reduce%20a%20%E2%82%AC151%20million%20tax%20bill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20Anil%20Ambani%20eventually%20was%20asked%20to%20pay%20was%20a%20greatly%20reduced%20amount%2C%20%E2%82%AC%206.6%20million%2C%20the%20report%20says%20%E2%80%93%20a%20sum%20that%20was%20close%20to%20the%20amount%20the%20Indian%20businessman%20had%20proposed%20as%20a%20settlement%20with%20the%20tax%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmbani%20was%20with%20Modi%20in%20France%20in%202015%2C%20during%20the%20visit%20where%20the%20prime%20minister%20decided%20to%20scrap%20an%20earlier%20deal%20for%20co-production%20of%20126%20Rafales%20with%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Ltd%20with%20one%20for%20the%20outright%20purchase%20of%2036%20aircraft%20from%20the%20French%20manufacturer%20Dassault.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20found%20evidence%20of%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter%20in%20confidential%20documents%20gathered%20by%20France%E2%80%99s%20tax%20administration.%20Its%20sources%20said%20that%20some%20of%20these%20have%20been%20added%20to%20evidence%20collected%20in%20the%20French%20judicial%20investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20surrounding%20the%202016%20sale%20of%2036%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20to%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmbani%20was%20brought%20into%20the%20deal%20as%20Rafale%E2%80%99s%20partner%20because%20that%20is%20what%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20insisted%20on%2C%20former%20French%20president%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Hollande%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frafale-deal-reliance-francois-hollande%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erevealed%20in%20a%202018%20interview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Dassault%20Aviation%20and%20Reliance%20have%20denied%20this%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20it%20had%20no%20say%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98commercial%20decision%E2%80%99%20taken%20by%20the%20French%20company.%20The%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20order%20a%20probe%20but%20the%20deal%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20current%20criminal%20investigation%20in%20France.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%E2%80%99s%20Rafale%20jets%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20military%20parade%20on%20July%2014%2C%20in%20which%20Modi%20is%20a%20guest%20of%20honour%20%E2%80%93%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20quarters%20in%20France%20who%20have%20cited%20the%20downslide%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMacron%20role%20raises%20eyebrows%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20says%20that%20as%20the%20Rafale%20deal%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20Reliance%20would%20be%20the%20main%20beneficiary%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20was%20being%20worked%20out%20during%202015%2C%20Anil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Flag%20Atlantic%20France%20was%20granted%20a%20%E2%82%AC%20144-million%20tax%20reduction.%20This%20action%20came%20after%20he%20wrote%20to%20ministers%20Sapin%20and%20Macron%20on%20April%2014%2C%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Sapin%20was%20finance%20minister%20and%20had%20direct%20control%20over%20the%20tax%20department%2C%20the%20report%20highlights%20that%20%E2%80%9CMacron%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20raises%20questions%20because%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20had%20no%20authority%20over%20the%20public%20finances%20directorate%2C%20the%20Direction%20G%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale%20des%20Finances%20Publiques%20(DGFIP).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20tax%20reduction%20was%20first%20reported%20by%20French%20daily%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Feconomie%2Farticle%2F2019%2F04%2F13%2Fcomment-la-france-a-efface-la-dette-fiscale-d-un-industriel-indien-associe-de-dassault_5449659_3234.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELe%20Monde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20had%20further%20quoted%20an%20unnamed%20Reliance%20employee%20as%20having%20said%20that%20he%20and%20Anil%20Ambani%20had%20met%20Macron%20at%20his%20office%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20the%20tax%20problem%20was%20settled%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20to%20his%20administration%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMacron%20and%20his%20office%20have%20not%20directly%20addressed%20questions%20on%20this.%20Macron%E2%80%99s%20former%20advisors%20at%20the%20economy%20ministry%20had%20told%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Le%20Monde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20had%20no%20recollection%20of%20a%20meeting%20between%20him%20and%20Ambani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESapin%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20recollection%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20possible%20thing%20that%20my%20cabinet%20may%20have%20done%20is%20to%20transfer%20the%20correspondence%20to%20the%20DGFIP%20for%20%5B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%5D%20study%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20highlights%20how%20Reliance%20Flag%20Atlantic%20France%2C%20which%20operated%20a%20cross-Atlantic%20underwater%20telecommunications%20cable%20linking%20France%20and%20the%20US%2C%20drew%20the%20French%20tax%20inspection%20directorate%E2%80%99s%20attention%20with%20its%20alleged%20tax%20evasion%20and%20avoidance%20practices.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReliance%20artificially%20transferred%20the%20profits%20from%20its%20French%20subsidiary%20to%20the%20mother%20company%20of%20its%20telecommunications%20activities%2C%20Reliance%20Globalcom%20Limited%2C%20which%20is%20registered%20in%20Bermuda%2C%20the%20British%20overseas%20territory%20which%20until%20recently%20featured%20on%20the%20European%20Union%E2%80%99s%20blacklist%20of%20non-cooperative%20tax%20havens%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98trump%20card%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrench%20tax%20authorities%20pored%20over%20detailed%20documents%20on%20Reliance%20Flag%20Atlantic%20France%E2%80%99s%20internal%20operations%20to%20determine%20that%20it%20owed%20them%20%E2%82%AC%20151%20million%20in%20taxes%20and%20penalties%20for%20the%202008-2012%20period.%20This%20amount%20is%20high%20largely%20thanks%20to%20a%20taxing%20strategy.%20As%20an%20expert%20told%20Mediapart%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tax%20authorities%20come%20up%20with%20%5Bthis%5D%20atomic%20weapon%20to%20push%20the%20company%20into%20providing%20the%20documents%20and%20reach%20an%20amicable%20settlement.%20It%20is%20therefore%20normal%20that%20there%20is%20a%20very%20steep%20reduction%20of%20the%20tax%20due%20if%20the%20company%20finally%20plays%20the%20game.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202014%2C%20Reliance%20provided%20documents%20and%20in%20early%202015%20proposed%20that%20it%20pay%20%E2%82%AC%206.2%20million.%20French%20authorities%20said%20this%20was%20too%20little.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20Ambani%20had%20a%20trump%20card%20to%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20March%202015%2C%20Reliance%20secretly%20became%20designated%20as%20Dassault%E2%80%99s%20new%20principal%20Indian%20local%20partner%20in%20the%20as-yet%20unsigned%20Rafale%20contract%2C%20undoing%20the%20Indian%20government-owned%20HAL%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20in%20this%20role%20three%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20in%20April%202015%2C%20Modi%20visited%20France%20with%20Anil%20Ambani.%20Thus%2C%20Mediapart%20notes%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20probability%2C%20with%20the%20Rafale%20deal%20still%20not%20inked%2C%20the%20French%20authorities%20would%20have%20been%20cautious%20not%20to%20upset%20Ambani%2C%20whose%20group%20was%20appointed%20as%20Dassault%E2%80%99s%20new%20principal%20partner%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20as%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Hollande%20confirmed%20in%20a%20previous%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F210918%2Ffrancois-hollande-his-partner-s-film-and-french-fighter-jet-sale-india%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Einterview%20with%20Mediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20France%20%E2%80%9Cdidn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20choice%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20matter.%20The%20Indian%20government%2C%20Reliance%20and%20Dassault%20all%20denied%20the%20former%20French%20president%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20events.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20dated%20April%2014%2C%202015%2C%20named%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20pleased%20with%20the%20strong%20momentum%20of%20bilateral%20exchanges%20between%20our%20governments%20led%20personally%20by%20Visionary%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20Mr.%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20France%20on%2010%20and%2011th%20April%202015%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20began.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20it%2C%20Anil%20Ambani%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20put%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20and%20unreasonable%20situation%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20tax%20amount.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20requested%20that%20the%20matter%20may%20kindly%20be%20reviewed%20in%20a%20fair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20transparent%20manner%2C%20and%20the%20highly%20unjust%20and%20unfair%20tax%20demands%20proposed%20as%20above%20may%20kindly%20be%20quashed%2C%20to%20give%20reassurance%20to%20Indian%20investors%20like%20Reliance%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20subjected%20to%20unnecessary%20tax%20litigation%20and%20high-pitched%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETax%20deal%20struck%20in%20a%20week%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reaction%20to%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20letter%20was%20swift%2C%20as%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20on%20April%2020%2C%202015%2C%20the%20central%20directorate%20of%20the%20tax%20inspection%20services%20wrote%20to%20its%20regional%20office%20asking%20for%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Reliance%20case%20file%20%E2%80%9Cfollowing%20the%20written%20request%20by%20the%20company%20(Indian%20CEO)%20made%20directly%20to%20the%20minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20Sapin.%20The%20documents%20were%20sent%20the%20very%20same%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20other%20French%20subsidiary%2C%20Reliance%20France%2C%20wrote%20to%20Sapin%2C%20with%20copies%20sent%20to%20Macron%2C%20Ambani%20and%20also%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambassador.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20pleased%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20an%20agreement%20has%20been%20reached%20on%20the%20terms%20of%20a%20settlement%20with%20the%20French%20Tax%20Authorities%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20and%20that%2C%20in%20our%20opinion%2C%20this%20represents%20an%20equitable%20and%20appropriate%20settlement%20in%20all%20the%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20requested%20by%20Mr.%20Anil%20Ambani%20to%20advise%20you%20that%20(a)%20we%20do%20not%20require%20any%20further%20assistance%20from%20your%20department%20and%20(b)%20the%20request%20set%20out%20in%20his%20letter%20of%20April%2014%2C%202015%20is%20hereby%20withdrawn.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20also%20concluded%20by%20thanking%20Sapin%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20your%20time%20and%20attention%20to%20this%20matter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20October%202022%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20resolved%20with%20Reliance%E2%80%99s%20deal%20with%20tax%20services%20formally%20signed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Mediapart%E2%80%99s%20source%20at%20the%20economy%20and%20finance%20ministry%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter%20%E2%80%9Chad%20no%20effect%20on%20the%20final%20settlement%2C%E2%80%9D%20experts%20consulted%20by%20the%20reporter%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20reduction%20may%20be%20justifiable%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20penalties%20were%20imposed%20on%20the%20debt%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20affecting%20a%20gain%20of%20around%201%20million%20euros%20%E2%80%93%20pointed%20to%20favourable%20treatment.%20Further%2C%20Reliance%20was%20deemed%20as%20having%20acted%20in%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20faith%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20experts%20said%20were%20odd%20given%20that%20it%20used%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstructure%20of%20aggressive%20tax%20optimisation%20in%20a%20tax%20haven.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689145304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12123012%2FUntitled-design-15-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frafale-corruption-anil-ambani-france-magistrate-tax%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%20news%20site%20also%20reveals%20letter%20Anil%20Ambani%20sent%20Macron%20and%20France's%20finance%20minister%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%202015%20Paris%20visit%2C%20seeking%20reduction%20in%20%E2%82%AC151%20million%20tax%20bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frafale-corruption-anil-ambani-france-magistrate-tax%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22French%20Magistrate%20Seeks%20India%E2%80%99s%20Cooperation%20in%20Rafale%20Corruption%20Probe%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12123012%2FUntitled-design-15-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Days%20ahead%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20France%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F120723%2Frafale-papers-how-indian-tycoon-sought-help-macron-and-finance-minister-over-tax-bill%5C%22%3EFrench%20news%20portal%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F120723%2Frafale-papers-how-indian-tycoon-sought-help-macron-and-finance-minister-over-tax-bill%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F120723%2Frafale-papers-how-indian-tycoon-sought-help-macron-and-finance-minister-over-tax-bill%5C%22%3E%20has%20revealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Paris%20magistrates%20have%20sent%20an%20official%20request%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20seeking%20its%20cooperation%20with%20an%20ongoing%20investigation%20into%20payments%20allegedly%20made%20in%20India%20by%20Dassault%20Aviation%20as%20part%20of%20the%202015-16%20deal%20for%20the%20sale%20of%2036%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20magistrates%20are%20notably%20interested%20in%20studying%20the%20case%20files%20of%20two%20Indian%20investigations%20which%2C%20as%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Frafale-false-invoices-sushen-gupta-mediapart%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20previously%20revealed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20detail%20evidence%20that%20Dassault%20secretly%20paid%20several%20million%20euros%20to%20Indian%20based%20business%20intermediary%20Sushen%20Gupta%20in%20its%20attempts%20to%20secure%20the%20deal%20signed%20in%202016%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%2C%20written%20by%20Yann%20Phillipin%2C%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20not%20immediately%20known%20what%20the%20Indian%20response%20will%20be.%20Requests%20of%20this%20kind%20are%20usually%20channeled%20through%20the%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20and%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20concerned%20department%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20most%20likely%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DOPT)%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%2C%20which%20look%20after%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Paris%20seeking%20information%20on%20the%20status%20of%20the%20French%20request%20and%20this%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20a%20reply%20is%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20is%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Fagustawestland-case-middleman-sushen-gupta-held-classified-papers-of-mod-iaf-and-hal-ed-claims%2Farticleshow%2F69626197.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20currently%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20VVIP%20chopper%20scam.%20Reports%20published%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202021%20exposed%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20deep%20business%20connections%20to%20Dassault%20and%20Thales%20over%20a%2015-year%20period%2C%20which%20allegedly%20involved%20paying%20him%20%E2%80%9Cseveral%20million%20euros%20in%20secret%20commissions%20to%20offshore%20accounts%20and%20shell%20companies%E2%80%9D%20using%20inflated%20invoices%20for%20software%20consulting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20explosive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20story%20also%20looks%20at%20another%20part%20of%20the%20Rafale%20puzzle%20%E2%80%93%20the%20tax%20reduction%20Reliance%20Group%20billionaire%20Anil%20Ambani%20secured%20from%20France%20in%202015.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reveals%20how%20Ambani%20wrote%20to%20French%20economics%20minister%20(and%20now%20president)%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20finance%20minister%20Michel%20Sapin%2C%20requesting%20their%20personal%20intervention%20to%20reduce%20a%20%E2%82%AC151%20million%20tax%20bill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20Anil%20Ambani%20eventually%20was%20asked%20to%20pay%20was%20a%20greatly%20reduced%20amount%2C%20%E2%82%AC%206.6%20million%2C%20the%20report%20says%20%E2%80%93%20a%20sum%20that%20was%20close%20to%20the%20amount%20the%20Indian%20businessman%20had%20proposed%20as%20a%20settlement%20with%20the%20tax%20authorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmbani%20was%20with%20Modi%20in%20France%20in%202015%2C%20during%20the%20visit%20where%20the%20prime%20minister%20decided%20to%20scrap%20an%20earlier%20deal%20for%20co-production%20of%20126%20Rafales%20with%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Ltd%20with%20one%20for%20the%20outright%20purchase%20of%2036%20aircraft%20from%20the%20French%20manufacturer%20Dassault.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20found%20evidence%20of%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter%20in%20confidential%20documents%20gathered%20by%20France%E2%80%99s%20tax%20administration.%20Its%20sources%20said%20that%20some%20of%20these%20have%20been%20added%20to%20evidence%20collected%20in%20the%20French%20judicial%20investigation%20into%20the%20corruption%20allegations%20surrounding%20the%202016%20sale%20of%2036%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20to%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmbani%20was%20brought%20into%20the%20deal%20as%20Rafale%E2%80%99s%20partner%20because%20that%20is%20what%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20insisted%20on%2C%20former%20French%20president%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Hollande%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frafale-deal-reliance-francois-hollande%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erevealed%20in%20a%202018%20interview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Dassault%20Aviation%20and%20Reliance%20have%20denied%20this%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20it%20had%20no%20say%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98commercial%20decision%E2%80%99%20taken%20by%20the%20French%20company.%20The%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20order%20a%20probe%20but%20the%20deal%20is%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20current%20criminal%20investigation%20in%20France.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%E2%80%99s%20Rafale%20jets%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20military%20parade%20on%20July%2014%2C%20in%20which%20Modi%20is%20a%20guest%20of%20honour%20%E2%80%93%20a%20decision%20that%20has%20been%20criticised%20by%20quarters%20in%20France%20who%20have%20cited%20the%20downslide%20of%20human%20rights%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMacron%20role%20raises%20eyebrows%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20says%20that%20as%20the%20Rafale%20deal%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20Reliance%20would%20be%20the%20main%20beneficiary%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20was%20being%20worked%20out%20during%202015%2C%20Anil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20Flag%20Atlantic%20France%20was%20granted%20a%20144-million%20euro%20tax%20reduction.%20This%20action%20came%20after%20he%20wrote%20to%20ministers%20Sapin%20and%20Macron%20on%20April%2014%2C%202015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Sapin%20was%20finance%20minister%20and%20had%20direct%20control%20over%20the%20tax%20department%2C%20the%20report%20highlights%20that%20%E2%80%9CMacron%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20raises%20questions%20because%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20he%20had%20no%20authority%20over%20the%20public%20finances%20directorate%2C%20the%20Direction%20G%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale%20des%20Finances%20Publiques%20(DGFIP).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20tax%20reduction%20was%20first%20reported%20by%20French%20daily%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lemonde.fr%2Feconomie%2Farticle%2F2019%2F04%2F13%2Fcomment-la-france-a-efface-la-dette-fiscale-d-un-industriel-indien-associe-de-dassault_5449659_3234.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELe%20Monde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20had%20further%20quoted%20an%20unnamed%20Reliance%20employee%20as%20having%20said%20that%20he%20and%20Anil%20Ambani%20had%20met%20Macron%20at%20his%20office%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhere%20the%20tax%20problem%20was%20settled%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20to%20his%20administration%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMacron%20and%20his%20office%20have%20not%20directly%20addressed%20questions%20on%20this.%20Macron%E2%80%99s%20former%20advisors%20at%20the%20economy%20ministry%20had%20told%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Le%20Monde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20had%20no%20recollection%20of%20a%20meeting%20between%20him%20and%20Ambani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESapin%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20recollection%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20possible%20thing%20that%20my%20cabinet%20may%20have%20done%20is%20to%20transfer%20the%20correspondence%20to%20the%20DGFIP%20for%20%5B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%5D%20study%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20highlights%20how%20Reliance%20Flag%20Atlantic%20France%2C%20which%20operated%20a%20cross-Atlantic%20underwater%20telecommunications%20cable%20linking%20France%20and%20the%20US%2C%20drew%20the%20French%20tax%20inspection%20directorate%E2%80%99s%20attention%20with%20its%20alleged%20tax%20evasion%20and%20avoidance%20practices.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReliance%20artificially%20transferred%20the%20profits%20from%20its%20French%20subsidiary%20to%20the%20mother%20company%20of%20its%20telecommunications%20activities%2C%20Reliance%20Globalcom%20Limited%2C%20which%20is%20registered%20in%20Bermuda%2C%20the%20British%20overseas%20territory%20which%20until%20recently%20featured%20on%20the%20European%20Union%E2%80%99s%20blacklist%20of%20non-cooperative%20tax%20havens%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98trump%20card%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrench%20tax%20authorities%20pored%20over%20detailed%20documents%20on%20Reliance%20Flag%20Atlantic%20France%E2%80%99s%20internal%20operations%20to%20determine%20that%20it%20owed%20them%20151%20million%20euros%20in%20taxes%20and%20penalties%20for%20the%202008-2012%20period.%20This%20amount%20is%20high%20largely%20thanks%20to%20a%20taxing%20strategy.%20As%20an%20expert%20told%20Mediapart%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tax%20authorities%20come%20up%20with%20%5Bthis%5D%20atomic%20weapon%20to%20push%20the%20company%20into%20providing%20the%20documents%20and%20reach%20an%20amicable%20settlement.%20It%20is%20therefore%20normal%20that%20there%20is%20a%20very%20steep%20reduction%20of%20the%20tax%20due%20if%20the%20company%20finally%20plays%20the%20game.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202014%2C%20Reliance%20provided%20documents%20and%20in%20early%202015%20proposed%20that%20it%20pay%206.2%20million%20euros.%20French%20authorities%20said%20this%20was%20too%20little.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20Ambani%20had%20a%20trump%20card%20to%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20March%202015%2C%20Reliance%20secretly%20became%20designated%20as%20Dassault%E2%80%99s%20new%20principal%20Indian%20local%20partner%20in%20the%20as-yet%20unsigned%20Rafale%20contract%2C%20undoing%20the%20Indian%20government-owned%20HAL%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20in%20this%20role%20three%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20in%20April%202015%2C%20Modi%20visited%20France%20with%20Anil%20Ambani.%20Thus%2C%20Mediapart%20notes%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20all%20probability%2C%20with%20the%20Rafale%20deal%20still%20not%20inked%2C%20the%20French%20authorities%20would%20have%20been%20cautious%20not%20to%20upset%20Ambani%2C%20whose%20group%20was%20appointed%20as%20Dassault%E2%80%99s%20new%20principal%20partner%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20as%20Fran%C3%A7ois%20Hollande%20confirmed%20in%20a%20previous%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F210918%2Ffrancois-hollande-his-partner-s-film-and-french-fighter-jet-sale-india%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Einterview%20with%20Mediapart%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20France%20%E2%80%9Cdidn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20choice%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20matter.%20The%20Indian%20government%2C%20Reliance%20and%20Dassault%20all%20denied%20the%20former%20French%20president%E2%80%99s%20version%20of%20events.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnil%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter%2C%20dated%20April%2014%2C%202015%2C%20named%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20pleased%20with%20the%20strong%20momentum%20of%20bilateral%20exchanges%20between%20our%20governments%20led%20personally%20by%20Visionary%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20Mr.%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20France%20on%2010%20and%2011th%20April%202015%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20began.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20it%2C%20Anil%20Ambani%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20put%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20and%20unreasonable%20situation%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20tax%20amount.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20requested%20that%20the%20matter%20may%20kindly%20be%20reviewed%20in%20a%20fair%2C%20reasonable%20and%20transparent%20manner%2C%20and%20the%20highly%20unjust%20and%20unfair%20tax%20demands%20proposed%20as%20above%20may%20kindly%20be%20quashed%2C%20to%20give%20reassurance%20to%20Indian%20investors%20like%20Reliance%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20subjected%20to%20unnecessary%20tax%20litigation%20and%20high-pitched%20demands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETax%20deal%20struck%20in%20a%20week%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reaction%20to%20Anil%E2%80%99s%20letter%20was%20swift%2C%20as%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20on%20April%2020%2C%202015%2C%20the%20central%20directorate%20of%20the%20tax%20inspection%20services%20wrote%20to%20its%20regional%20office%20asking%20for%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Reliance%20case%20file%20%E2%80%9Cfollowing%20the%20written%20request%20by%20the%20company%20(Indian%20CEO)%20made%20directly%20to%20the%20minister%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20a%20reference%20to%20Sapin.%20The%20documents%20were%20sent%20the%20very%20same%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20other%20French%20subsidiary%2C%20Reliance%20France%2C%20wrote%20to%20Sapin%2C%20with%20copies%20sent%20to%20Macron%2C%20Ambani%20and%20also%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambassador.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20pleased%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20an%20agreement%20has%20been%20reached%20on%20the%20terms%20of%20a%20settlement%20with%20the%20French%20Tax%20Authorities%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20and%20that%2C%20in%20our%20opinion%2C%20this%20represents%20an%20equitable%20and%20appropriate%20settlement%20in%20all%20the%20circumstances%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20requested%20by%20Mr.%20Anil%20Ambani%20to%20advise%20you%20that%20(a)%20we%20do%20not%20require%20any%20further%20assistance%20from%20your%20department%20and%20(b)%20the%20request%20set%20out%20in%20his%20letter%20of%20April%2014%2C%202015%20is%20hereby%20withdrawn.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20also%20concluded%20by%20thanking%20Sapin%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20your%20time%20and%20attention%20to%20this%20matter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20October%202022%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20resolved%20with%20Reliance%E2%80%99s%20deal%20with%20tax%20services%20formally%20signed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Mediapart%E2%80%99s%20source%20at%20the%20economy%20and%20finance%20ministry%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20letter%20%E2%80%9Chad%20no%20effect%20on%20the%20final%20settlement%2C%E2%80%9D%20experts%20consulted%20by%20the%20reporter%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20reduction%20may%20be%20justifiable%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20penalties%20were%20imposed%20on%20the%20debt%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20affecting%20a%20gain%20of%20around%201%20million%20euros%20%E2%80%93%20pointed%20to%20favourable%20treatment.%20Further%2C%20Reliance%20was%20deemed%20as%20having%20acted%20in%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20faith%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20experts%20said%20were%20odd%20given%20that%20it%20used%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstructure%20of%20aggressive%20tax%20optimisation%20in%20a%20tax%20haven.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689145304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12123012%2FUntitled-design-15-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frafale-corruption-anil-ambani-france-magistrate-tax%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22French%20news%20site%20also%20reveals%20letter%20Anil%20Ambani%20sent%20Macron%20and%20France's%20finance%20minister%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%202015%20Paris%20visit%2C%20seeking%20reduction%20in%20%E2%82%AC151%20million%20tax%20bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Frafale-corruption-anil-ambani-france-magistrate-tax%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Undaunted%20by%20adversities%20Jyoti%20'fulfilling%20papa's%20dream'%20on%20hockey%20field%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689145203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101690388%2Cimgsize-72442.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fhockey%2Ftop-stories%2Fundaunted-by-adversities-jyoti-chhatri-is-fulfilling-papas-dream-on-the-hockey-field%2Farticleshow%2F101690385.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Driving%20through%20the%20Chhend%20Colony%20in%20Rourkela%2C%20navigating%20a%20few%20narrow%20lanes%2C%20you%20land%20up%20in%20Panposh%20that%20has%20hockey%20dominating%20its%20history%20and%20geography.%20One%20of%20the%20serpentine%20turns%20leads%20you%20to%20the%20State%20Sports%20Hostel%2C%20which%20almost%20surprises%20you%20with%20a%20vast%20expanse%20of%20a%20compound%20in%20front%20of%20the%20gate%2C%20and%20the%20facility's%20body%20of%20work%20has%20only%20grown%20since%20its%20inception%20in%201985%2C%20giving%20India%20a%20number%20of%20international%20hockey%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JASPREET%20SAHNI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fhockey%2Ftop-stories%2Fundaunted-by-adversities-jyoti-chhatri-is-fulfilling-