0%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1678790942613180418%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoval%20spoke%20about%20Indian%20history%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20Islam%20in%20the%20region%20and%20the%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20he%20said%20India%20has%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmelting%20pot%20of%20cultures%2C%20religions%2C%20languages%20and%20ethnicities%E2%80%9D%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252F100094123640266%252Fvideos%252F844436120739529%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D4915%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSA%20said%20that%20India%20is%20an%20inclusive%20democracy%20which%20has%20provided%20space%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20regardless%20of%20religious%2C%20ethnic%20and%20cultural%20identities.%20%E2%80%9CAmongst%20the%20numerous%20religious%20groups%2C%20Islam%20occupies%20a%20unique%20and%20significant%20position%20of%20pride%2C%20with%20India%20being%20home%20to%20the%20second%20largest%20Muslim%20population%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20adding%20noting%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20equal%20in%20number%20to%20the%20cumulative%20population%20of%20more%20than%2033%20members%20of%20the%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20(OIC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OIC%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fram-navami-violence-oic-expresses-deep-concern-india-call-st