%20important%20events%20in%20the%201789%20French%20Revolution.%20Since%201880%2C%20it%20is%20marked%20with%20a%20military%20parade%20on%20the%20Champs-%C3%89lys%C3%A9es%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20occasional%20participation%20of%20foreign%20contingents.%20Indian%20soldiers%20took%20part%20in%20the%20parade%20in%202008%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20in%20attendance.%20Once%20again%2C%20Indian%20PM%20Modi%2C%20as%20the%20guest%20of%20honour%20at%20the%20parade%2C%20will%20witness%20a%20tri-service%20contingent%20parading%20through%20the%20main%20avenue%20of%20Paris.%20They%20will%20also%20take%20part%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Indian%20and%20French%20CEOs%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11203901%2F1080px-Fly_over_Bastille_Day_2017.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11203901%2F1080px-Fly_over_Bastille_Day_2017.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11203901%2F1080px-Fly_over_Bastille_Day_2017-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11203901%2F1080px-Fly_over_Bastille_Day_2017-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662719%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Patrouille%20de%20France%20with%20nine%20Alpha%20Jets%20over%20the%20Champs-%C3%89lys%C3%A9es%20in%20Paris%20in%202017.%20Photo%3A%20US%20Navy%2C%20Chief%20Petty%20Officer%20Michael%20McNabb%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20Public%20Domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20are%20the%20likely%20deliverables%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20was%20the%20cas