%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20Dr%20Mukul%20Verma%2C%20who%20works%20at%20Noida%E2%80%99s%20Apollo%20Hospital%2C%20also%20considered%20adding%20a%20greywater%20recycling%20system%20while%20constructing%20his%20new%20home%20in%20a%20hill%20village%20of%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Almora%20district.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20began%20using%20Jal%20Sevak%E2%80%99s%20device.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20village%2C%20there%20is%20no%20water%20supply%20in%20nearby%20areas.%20We%20are%20entirely%20dependent%20either%20on%20rainwater%20or%20irregular%20municipal%20water%20supply.%20Every%20month%2C%20I%20visit%20our%20home%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20a%20week.%20Today%2C%20I%20am%20able%20to%20save%20water%20by%20reusing%20it%20for%20toilet%20flushing%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229847%2Fgardening-tips-natural-greywater-recycling-indukanth-ragade-save-water-chennai-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eirrigating%20my%20crop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20the%20guilt%20%5Bof%20wastage%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Need%20more%20competitors%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20entrepreneurs%2C%20Abhijit%20wishes%20for%20more%20competitors%20in%20the%20market.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20hardly%20any%20dedicated%20company%20or%20individual%20working%20in%20this%20sector.%20We%20need%20similar%20products%20coming%20in%20the%20market%20so%20that%20more%20innovative%20ways%20are%20given%20thought%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhijit%20explains%20that%20greywater%20comprises%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20daily%20water%20use.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fgreywater-1-1688562760-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhijit%20explains%20that%20greywater%20comprises%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20daily%20water%20use.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20highlighting%20the%20limitations%20of%20greywater%20recycling%20systems%2C%20Abhijit%20says%20that%20space%20is%20a%20major%20constraint.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20we%20have%20to%20check%20where%20we%20can%20set%20up%20the%20tank%20to%20collect%20greywater.%20Generally%2C%20we%20set%20it%20up%20underground%20and%20in%20a%20basement.%20We%20get%20many%20queries%20from%20individual%20flat%20owners%2C%20but%20we%20can%20set%20up%20such%20a%20system%20for%20an%20entire%20building%2C%20as%20it%20would%20not%20be%20cost-effective%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20residential%20complexes%2C%20Abhijit%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20system%20into%20restaurants%2C%20institutes%2C%20canteens%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20are%20totally%20dependent%20on%20the%20monsoon%20every%20year%2C%20which%20has%20not%20failed%20us.%20But%20with%20changing%20weather%20patterns%20amid%20climate%20change%2C%20we%20are%20to%20get%20below%20average%20monsoon%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20