0language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20process%20takes%20about%2035%20minutes.%20We%20get%20cases%20of%20diabetes%2C%20malaria%20and%20dengue%2C%20gynaecological%20and%20neurological%20disorder%20issues%2C%20and%20even%20cancer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatients%20who%20cannot%20be%20treated%20by%20telemedicine%20are%20suggested%20hospitals%20in%20cities%20for%20physical%20examination.%20Sandeep%20says%20to%20ensure%20minimal%20financial%20burden%20on%20patients%2C%20he%20connects%20them%20through%20various%20government-run%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20ensure%20that%20their%20treatment%20does%20not%20stop%20because%20of%20financial%20constraints.%20In%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20care%20cases%2C%20we%20handhold%20our%20patients%20from%20day%20one%20till%20they%20are%20treated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20DigiSwasthya%20came%20to%20the%20rescue%20of%2022-year-old%20Manisha%20Kumari%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20a%20village%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20bone%20cancer%20in%20her%20knee%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20to%20a%20Varanasi%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20But%20the%20doctor%20said%20that%20my%20leg%20needs%20to%20be%20removed.%20I%20looked%20at%20my%20mother%20and%20I%20told%20her%20that%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20lead%20a%20life%20such%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fdigiswasthya-4-1688390529.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manisha%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20bone%20cancer%20in%20her%20knee%20in%202021%20and%20was%20told%20that%20her%20leg%20needs%20to%20be%20removed.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo